Inflict 1000 damage to your opponent. Draw 1 card. Then, if you drew by this effect, you can Set 1 "The Noodle Art of Savory" and/or 1 "The Noodle Art of Saucery" from your Graveyard in your Spell & Trap Zone.

160007039.name: Miso Instant the Special Noodle Ninja
160007039.description:
"Cross Promotion the Elite Noodle Ninja" + "Flavor Inspector"

[REQUIREMENT]
Shuffle 3 Pyro Type monsters from your Graveyard into the Deck.
[EFFECT]
This turn, this card gains 600 ATK, and if it attacks a Defense Position monster, inflict piercing battle damage (if the ATK of the attacking monster exceeds the DEF of the attack target, inflict the difference).

160007040.name: Hunter of Titans
160007040.description:
"Descendant of Titans" + "Babysitter Goat"

[REQUIREMENT]
Shuffle 1 Fiend Type Normal Monster from your Graveyard into the Deck.
[EFFECT]
Destroy 1 Spell/Trap Card on your opponent's field.

160007041.name: Fenriritter Sol
160007041.description:
"Sigurstate Sol" + "Connector Dog"

[REQUIREMENT]
Send the top 2 cards of your Deck to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Draw 1 card. Then, if your opponent has a monster on their field, you can Special Summon 1 Cyberse Type monster from your hand to your field face-up.

160007042.name: Supreme Marine Fortress Magnum Overbase
160007042.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Activate this card if your LP are lower than your opponent's.
[EFFECT]
While this card is face-up in the Field Zone, all face-up Level 7 or higher Machine Type monsters on the field gain 400 ATK, also face-up Level 10 Machine Type monsters on the field cannot be destroyed by the effects of Spell/Trap Cards.

160007043.name: Five Types of Assistance
160007043.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
If you have a face-up Warrior, Fairy, Beast, Winged Beast, or Reptile Type monster on your field.
[EFFECT]
Up to 2 face-up monsters on your field cannot be destroyed by the effects of your opponent's Trap Cards this turn.

160007044.name: Bizarrmor
160007044.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Place 3 Level 7 or higher monsters with different Types from your Graveyard on the top or bottom of the Deck in any order.
[EFFECT]
Add 1 Normal Monster from your Graveyard to your hand, then you can make 1 face-up monster on your opponent's field lose 1500 ATK until the end of this turn.

160007045.name: Shape of Aqua
160007045.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Send 1 Spell/Trap Card from your hand to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Special Summon 1 Fish, Sea Serpent, Thunder, or Aqua Type monster from your Graveyard to your field face-up. The monster Special Summoned by this effect loses 800 ATK until the end of this turn.

160007046.name: Stream of Elimination
160007046.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
You have a face-up Sea Serpent Type monster on your field.
[EFFECT]
Destroy 1 Spell/Trap Card on your opponent's field.

160007047.name: Feverous Spirit Stadium
160007047.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
None
[EFFECT]
While this card is face-up in the Field Zone, all face-up FIRE monsters on your field gain 400 ATK during your turn only, also all face-up FIRE monsters on your opponent's field gain 400 ATK during their turn only.

160007048.name: Hot Off the Press
160007048.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
If you have a face-up EARTH Machine Type monster on your field, send 1 EARTH Machine Type monster from your hand to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Your opponent takes the bottom 5 cards of their Deck and shows them. Inflict damage to your opponent equal to [the number of monsters among the shown cards] x 400. Your opponent places the shown cards on top of their Deck in any order.

160007049.name: Reprinter
160007049.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
You have a face-up Level 7 or higher EARTH Attribute Machine Type monster on your field.
[EFFECT]
Special Summon 1 "Printing Presser" from your Graveyard face-up to your field. This turn, the monster Special Summoned by this effect cannot attack directly.

160007050.name: The Noodle Art of Roastery
160007050.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
You have a face-up Level 7 or higher Pyro Type monster on your field.
[EFFECT]
All face-up Pyro Type monsters on your field gain ATK equal to [the number of Normal Monsters in the Graveyards] x 100 until the end of this turn.

160007051.name: The Noodle Art of Saucery
160007051.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Send cards from your hand to the Graveyard, up to the number of Pyro Type Normal Monsters in your Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Draw cards equal to [the number of cards sent to the Graveyard by the requirement of this effect]. Then, if you have a face-up Pyro Type Normal Monster on your field, you can draw 1 additional card.

160007052.name: Ship of Seven Treasures
160007052.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Send 1 monster from your hand to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Draw 1 card. Then, if you sent a Level 7 monster to the Graveyard by the requirement of this effect, you can draw 1 additional card.

160007053.name: Back Beat
160007053.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Shuffle 2 monsters from your Graveyard into the Deck.
[EFFECT]
Shuffle 2 to 7 monsters with the same Type from your opponent's Graveyard into the Deck. Then, if you shuffled 4 or more monsters by this effect, you can draw 1 card.

160007054.name: Stream
160007054.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
None
[EFFECT]
While this card is face-up in the Field Zone, all face-up Level 3 or lower Fish, Sea Serpent, Thunder, and Aqua Type monsters on the field gain 600 ATK/DEF.

160007055.name: Card Devastation
160007055.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
None
[EFFECT]
Each player with a hand sends their entire hand to the Graveyard, then you can make 1 face-up monster on your field gain ATK equal to [the number of cards sent to the Graveyard by this effect] x 300 until the end of this turn.

160007056.name: Shocking Comeback!!
160007056.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
When an opponent's Level 6 or higher monster declares an attack.
[EFFECT]
Gain LP equal to [the ATK of 1 Level 6 or lower Psychic Type monster in your Graveyard]. Then, if you gained 1000 or more LP by this effect, you can add that monster to your hand.

160007057.name: Pair Collision
160007057.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
When an opponent's monster declares an attack on your face-up Level 10 or higher monster.
[EFFECT]
Monsters cannot be destroyed by that battle.

160007058.name: Dolphin Counterattack
160007058.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
When an opponent's monster declares an attack targeting your face-up Fish or Sea Serpent Type monster, shuffle 1 "Umi" or "Big Umi" from your Graveyard into the Deck.
[EFFECT]
Destroy 1 face-up monster on your opponent's field with the highest ATK. Draw 1 card and show it. Then, if that card is "Umi" or "Big Umi", inflict 500 damage to your opponent.

160007059.name: Seastorm of Iruqua
160007059.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
When an opponent's monster declares a direct attack while you have "Umi" or "Big Umi" face-up on your field.
[EFFECT]
Change the battle positions of all face-up monsters on your opponent's field (Attack Position becomes face-up Defense Position, Defense Position becomes face-up Attack Position). Then, you can Special Summon 1 Sea Serpent Type Normal Monster from your Graveyard face-up to your field.

160007060.name: Gagaga Guts
160007060.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
When a monster on your field is destroyed by an opponent's card effect.
[EFFECT]
Special Summon 1 FIRE monster from your Graveyard to your field in face-up Defense Position. Then, if you Special Summoned "Player #39: Home Run Hitter" or "Player #99: Grand Slam Dragon" by this effect, you can destroy 1 monster on your opponent's field.

160007061.name: Requesting 9
160007061.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
When your monster is destroyed by an opponent's attack.
[EFFECT]
Gain 900 LP. Then, if you have 9 or more FIRE monsters in your Graveyard, you can Special Summon 1 "Player #39: Home Run Hitter" or "Player #99: Grand Slam Dragon" from your Graveyard to your field face-up.

160007062.name: Reporting from the Scene!
160007062.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
When an opponent's monster declares a direct attack, send 1 EARTH Machine Type monster from your hand to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Inflict 300 damage to your opponent. Then, if you inflicted damage to your opponent by this effect, you take no battle damage this turn.

160007063.name: Breaking News!
160007063.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
When a face-up Machine Type monster on your field is destroyed by an opponent's attack or card effect.
[EFFECT]
Inflict 300 damage to your opponent. Then, if you inflicted damage to your opponent by this effect, you can Special Summon up to 2 "ExPress Train" from your Graveyard to your field face-up.

160007064.name: Spiral Geyser
160007064.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
When your opponent Normal Summons or Sets a monster from the hand.
[EFFECT]
Inflict 400 damage to your opponent. This turn, your opponent cannot Tribute face-down monsters for a Tribute Summon.

160007065.name: Hardefense Mission
160007065.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
When an opponent's Level 8 or lower monster with 2500 or more original ATK declares an attack.
[EFFECT]
Destroy the attacking monster.

160008000.name: The Creator (Rush)
160008000.description:
This card cannot be Special Summoned from the Graveyard.

[REQUIREMENT]
You have cards in your hand.
[EFFECT]
Special Summon 1 monster from your Graveyard face-up to your field. Then, send 1 card from your hand to the Graveyard.

160008001.name: Dark Femtron
160008001.description: The source of the draconic tree that is connected to another providence. It conceals infinite branches that lead to an unseen world.

160008002.name: Snake Clown
160008002.description: An always cheerful and friendly snake. It fascinates the audience by dancing to the tune of a flute.

160008003.name: Ancient Lizard Warrior (Rush)
160008003.description: Before the dawn of man, this lizard warrior ruled supreme.

160008004.name: Armored Lizard (Rush)
160008004.description: A lizard with a very tough hide and a vicious bite.

160008005.name: Boosturtle
160008005.description: A turtle born from a plan of utter madness. It seems to move through space how it pleases using its booster rockets.

160008006.name: Pluggyfish
160008006.description: A lifeform whose body is made out of a jellyfish and plugs. Its way of life is full of mysteries.

160008007.name: Anglercoilfish
160008007.description: A goosefish with a developed organ that produces electricity. It attacks its enemies with electric shocks and its sharp fangs.

160008008.name: Antsgiving
160008008.description: Ants who always give thanks to their comrades for their support. They're determined to further increase the number of their allies.

160008009.name: Lauan Adventurers
160008009.description: Adventurers who seek unknown land. They originally competed to see how far they could fly, but at some point they began to travel together.

160008010.name: Germalewe
160008010.description: A violent entity that lives in the world of flames. Not even the bones of its prey are left behind.

160008011.name: Sevens Road Sorcerer
160008011.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Send 3 face-up monsters from your field to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Special Summon 1 Level 7 or lower Spellcaster Type monster from your Graveyard face-up to your field. Then, if you Special Summoned "Sevens Road Magician" by this effect, you can Special Summon 1 "Sevens Road Witch" from your Graveyard face-up to your field.

160008012.name: Rhythmical Performer
160008012.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Send the top card of your Deck to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Your opponent sends the top card of their Deck to the Graveyard. Then, if they sent a Spell/Trap Card to the Graveyard by this effect, you can draw 1 card.

160008013.name: Executie Feena
160008013.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
If your opponent has a face-up monster with 1700 or more ATK on their field, send the top card of your Deck to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
All face-up monsters on your field gain 200 ATK until the end of this turn.

160008014.name: Shearkyrie the Celestial Seamstress
160008014.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
If you have no other monsters on your field, place 1 card from your hand on the bottom of the Deck.
[EFFECT]
Special Summon 1 Fairy Type monster with 0 ATK from your Graveyard face-up to your field.

160008015.name: Mecha Ambulator
160008015.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
You Normal Summoned this card this turn and have a face-up WIND Attribute Normal Monster on your field.
[EFFECT]
Add 1 "Following World" from your Graveyard to your hand.

160008016.name: Player C39: Home Run Smasher
160008016.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Shuffle 3 Level 4 FIRE Attribute monsters from your Graveyard into the Deck.
[EFFECT]
This card gains 1500 ATK until the end of this turn. Then, if your LP are 1000 or lower, you can make 1 face-up monster on your opponent's field lose 3000 ATK until the end of this turn.

160008017.name: Kamaleon
160008017.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Pay 300 LP.
[EFFECT]
Send the top 3 cards of your Deck to the Graveyard. Then, if a Reptile Type Normal Monster(s) is among the cards sent, add 1 Reptile Type Normal Monster from your Graveyard to your hand. You can only attack with Reptile Type monsters the turn you activated this effect.

160008018.name: Clawmeleon
160008018.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
If your opponent has a face-down monster on their field, send the top 2 cards of your Deck to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Choose 1 face-up Level 7 or higher Reptile Type monster on your field. If it attacks a Defense Position monster this turn, inflict piercing battle damage (if the ATK of the attacking monster exceeds the DEF of the attack target, inflict the difference).

160008019.name: Fiery Infernleon
160008019.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
If your LP are lower than your opponent's, pay 600 LP.
[EFFECT]
Send the top 3 cards of your Deck to the Graveyard. Then, if a Reptile Type monster(s) is among the cards sent, you can Special Summon 1 Level 6 or lower Reptile Type Normal Monster from your Graveyard face-up to your field.

160008020.name: Metal Megaleon
160008020.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
If your LP are lower than your opponent's, pay 600 LP.
[EFFECT]
Send the top 3 cards of your Deck to the Graveyard. This card gains 600 ATK until the end of this turn.

160008021.name: Predator Ganleon
160008021.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
If your LP are 1000 or lower, send the top 5 cards of your Deck to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
This card gains ATK equal to [the difference between your LP and your opponent's LP] until the end of this turn.

160008022.name: Ecdysis Caesarleon
160008022.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
None
[CONTINUOUS EFFECT]
This card gains ATK equal to [the number of cards in your Graveyard] x 100.

160008023.name: Spyturtle
160008023.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Send the top card of your Deck to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Reduce the Level of 1 face-up Level 3-8 monster on your opponent's field by 2 until the end of this turn.

160008024.name: Rocketortoise Modularchelon
160008024.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Send up to 2 other face-up Reptile Type monsters from your field to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
This card gains ATK equal to [the number of monsters sent to the Graveyard to meet the requirement] x 700 until the end of this turn.

160008025.name: Zap Zap Octospark
160008025.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
You Normal Summoned this card this turn and have a face-up Thunder Type Normal Monster on your field.
[EFFECT]
This card gains 400 ATK until the end of this turn. Then, inflict 400 damage to your opponent.

160008026.name: Lightning Bringer Spirit
160008026.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Send the top card of your Deck to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Shuffle 1 card from your opponent's Graveyard into the Deck. Then, if you shuffled a Spell/Trap Card by this effect, you can shuffle 1 additional card from your opponent's Graveyard into the Deck.

160008027.name: Sensor Duckbill
160008027.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Place 1 card from your hand on the bottom of the Deck.
[EFFECT]
Add 1 Level 5 or higher Thunder Type monster from your Graveyard to your hand.

160008028.name: Emitter Stag
160008028.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Send the top card of your Deck to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Reduce the Level of 1 face-up Level 5 or higher Thunder Type monster on your field by 4 until the end of this turn. Then, inflict 400 damage to your opponent.

160008029.name: Blast Jaws
160008029.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
If your opponent has 1 or less cards in their hand, shuffle 1 Thunder Type monster from your Graveyard into the Deck.
[EFFECT]
1 face-up Thunder Type monster on your field gains 400 ATK until the end of this turn.

160008030.name: Stormbolt Destroyer
160008030.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Your opponent has 2 or less cards in their hand.
[EFFECT]
Special Summon 1 Level 4 or lower Thunder Type Normal Monster from your Graveyard face-up to your field.

160008031.name: Thunder Cavalry Triggerdrago
160008031.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Send the top card of your Deck to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
This card gains 300 ATK until the end of this turn. Also, if your opponent has no cards in their hand, this card inflicts piercing battle damage (if the ATK of the attacking monster exceeds the DEF of the attack target, inflict the difference), if it attacks a Defense Position monster this turn.

160008032.name: Master of the Sevens Road
160008032.description:
"Sevens Road Magician" + "Sevens Road Witch"

[REQUIREMENT]
None
[CONTINUOUS EFFECT]
This card gains ATK equal to [the number of DARK Attribute Spellcaster Type monsters with different names in your Graveyard] x 300. If you have 7 or more DARK Attribute Spellcaster Type monsters in your Graveyard, this card inflicts piercing battle damage (if the ATK of the attacking monster exceeds the DEF of the attack target, inflict the difference), if it attacks a Defense Position monster.

160008033.name: Hazy Strike Dragon Miragiastar F
160008033.description:
"Illusion Strike Dragon Miragias" + "The Dragon"

[REQUIREMENT]
Send the top card of your Deck to the Graveyard.
[MULTI-CHOICE EFFECT]
● Up to 3 face-up monsters on your opponent's field lose 1500 ATK until the end of this turn. This turn, this card can make up to 2 attacks on monsters.
● This turn, this card can attack directly.

160008034.name: Endless Romance Blitz
160008034.description:
"Folder Blitz the Infinite Dream" + "Romanpick"

[REQUIREMENT]
Shuffle 1 "Folder Blitz the Infinite Dream" and 1 "Romanpick" from your Graveyard into the Deck.
[MULTI-CHOICE EFFECT]
● Inflict 1500 damage to your opponent.
● Draw 3 cards. Then, send 2 cards from your hand to the Graveyard.

160008035.name: Hero of the Assist
160008035.description:
"Hero of the Yeast" + "Hero of the Yeast"

[REQUIREMENT]
None
[EFFECT]
Add 1 Level 4 or lower Warrior Type Normal Monster from your Graveyard to your hand.

160008036.name: Semeterasu the Divine Ruler
160008036.description:
"Semeruler the Dark Summoner" + "Needlkyrie the Celestia Seamstress"

[REQUIREMENT]
None
[MULTI-CHOICE EFFECT]
● Special Summon 1 Level 8 or lower Warrior or Fairy Type monster from your Graveyard face-up to your field.
● Shuffle monsters from your opponent's Graveyard into the Deck, up to [the number of monsters with 0 ATK in your Graveyard].

160008037.name: Meika Etraynze the Shadow Flower Venus
160008037.description:
"Etraynze the Shadow Flower Ninja" + "Etraynze the Shadow Flower Ninja"

[REQUIREMENT]
None
[EFFECT]
Special Summon 1 Level 8 or lower Plant Type monster from your hand or your Graveyard face-up to your field.

160008038.name: Durga the Shadow Flower Submarine
160008038.description:
"Gatling the Shadow Flower Shinobi" + "Lindo the Shadow Flower Warrior"

[REQUIREMENT]
Your opponent has 2 or more monsters on their field.
[EFFECT]
Destroy all face-up Level 6 or higher monsters on your opponent's field.

160008039.name: Metarion King Cobrastar
160008039.description:
"Imaginary Actor" + "Snake Clown"

[REQUIREMENT]
Send 1 card from your hand to the Graveyard.
[MULTI-CHOICE EFFECT]
● Draw 2 cards. Then, send 1 card from your hand to the Graveyard.
● Up to 3 face-up Reptile Type monsters on your opponent's field lose 1000 ATK/DEF until the end of this turn. This card can attack twice during this turn.

160008040.name: Poseigyon Advencharger
160008040.description:
"Anglercoilfish" + "Pluggyfish"

[REQUIREMENT]
Send the top card of your Deck to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
All face-up Thunder Type monsters on your field gain 400 ATK until the end of this turn.

160008041.name: Showering Seaferno
160008041.description:
"Zap Zap Octospark" + "Pluggyfish"

[REQUIREMENT]
None
[EFFECT]
Add 1 "Zapzap Octospark" from your Graveyard to your hand. Then, inflict 800 damage to your opponent. Then, if your opponent has a face-up Level 8 monster on their field, this turn, this card gains 800 ATK and all face-up Level 8 monsters on your opponent's field lose 800 ATK.

160008042.name: Prime Roast Beef Horseman
160008042.description:
"Barbeque Ox" + "Mystic Roastman"

[REQUIREMENT]
During your Main Phase that you Special Summoned this card, place 4 FIRE Attribute Beast Type monsters from your Graveyard on top of your Deck in any order.
[EFFECT]
Add up to 1 each of "Best Bite", "B・B・Q", and "Wild Kitchen" from your Graveyard to your hand.

160008043.name: Hormone GunMcQueen, the Magnificent Shichirin
160008043.description:
"Shichirin Samurai - Kushiro the Skewer Master" + "Flavor Inspector"

[REQUIREMENT]
Shuffle 2 "Shichirin Samurai - Kushiro the Skewer Master" and/or "Flavor Inspector" from your Graveyard into the Deck.
[EFFECT]
Destroy all face-up Level 9 or lower non-FIRE Attribute monsters on your opponent's field.

160008044.name: Ether Fast Striker
160008044.description:
"Ether Seeker" + "Ether Finder"

[REQUIREMENT]
Place 1 "Fusion" from your Graveyard on either the top or bottom of your Deck.
[EFFECT]
This card gains 600 ATK until the end of this turn. Then, you can place 1 Normal Monster from your Graveyard on top of your Deck.

160008045.name: Vulcan Ignite Hyperdrive
160008045.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
You have a face-up FIRE Attribute Warrior Type Maximum Monster on your field.
[EFFECT]
Inflict 800 damage to your opponent. Then, if you have a monster in Maximum Mode on your field, you can destroy 1 card on your opponent's field.

160008046.name: Royal Rebel's Echo
160008046.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Place 1 card from your hand on the bottom of the Deck.
[EFFECT]
Special Summon 1 Level 7 or lower Fiend Type monster with 0 DEF from your hand or your Graveyard face-up to your field. Then, if you Special Summoned a Level 7 monster by this effect, you can add 1 Fiend Type monster from your Graveyard to your hand.

160008047.name: Shadow Flower Flurry
160008047.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Send 1 face-up Plant Type monster from your field to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Change 1 Defense Position monster on either field to face-up Attack Position. Then, you can draw 1 card.

160008048.name: Shadow Flower Wish
160008048.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
If you have a Plant Type monster in your Graveyard, send 2 face-up Plant Type monsters from your field to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Special Summon 1 Plant Type monster from your Graveyard face-up to your field.

160008049.name: Tag-Up-Magic Sacrifice Force
160008049.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Send 1 face-up FIRE Attribute monster from your field to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Special Summon 1 Level 8 FIRE Attribute monster from your hand face-up to your field. Then, if you sent a Level 8 monster to the Graveyard to meet the requirement, you can destroy 1 Spell/Trap Card on your opponent's field.

160008050.name: Bobbleheader
160008050.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
None
[EFFECT]
Add up to 2 "Feverous Spirit Stadium" and/or "Tag-Up-Magic Sacrifice Force" from your Graveyard to your hand.

160008051.name: Release Wrath
160008051.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
If your opponent has a monster on their field, pay 1000 LP.
[EFFECT]
Send the top 5 cards of your Deck to the Graveyard. Then, if a Reptile Type monster(s) is among the cards sent, you can make 1 face-up Reptile Type monster on your field gain ATK equal to [the number of Reptile Type monsters sent to the Graveyard by this effect] x 200 until the end of this turn.

160008052.name: Fire Wrath
160008052.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Send 2 Reptile Type monsters from your hand to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Destroy 1 face-up monster on your opponent's field with an equal or lower Level than [the total Level of the monsters sent to the Graveyard to meet the requirement].

160008053.name: Spy Observation
160008053.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
You have 2 or more face-up Reptile Type monsters on your field.
[EFFECT]
Excavate the top card of your Deck. Then, place the excavated card on either the top or bottom of your Deck. Then, you can destroy 1 Spell/Trap Card on your opponent's field.

160008054.name: Destructurtle Meteor
160008054.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
None
[EFFECT]
2 face-up Reptile Type monsters on your field and 1 face-up Level 8 or lower monster on your opponent's field lose 1500 ATK until the end of this turn.

160008055.name: Clapping Thunder
160008055.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
You have 2 or more face-up Thunder Type monsters on your field.
[EFFECT]
All face-up monsters on your opponent's field lose 400 ATK/DEF until the end of this turn. Then, if you have 3 Thunder Type monsters on your field, you can draw 1 card.

160008056.name: Trailblitzing Thunderblast
160008056.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
You have a face-up Thunder Type monster on your field.
[EFFECT]
Destroy 1 Spell/Trap Card on your opponent's field.

160008057.name: Parallel Birth Gate
160008057.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
None
[EFFECT]
Send the top card of your Deck to the Graveyard. Then, if you have no cards in your hand, you can Special Summon up to 2 Normal Monsters from your Graveyard face-up to your field.

160008058.name: Makiu, the Magical Mist (Rush)
160008058.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
None
[EFFECT]
Destroy all face-up monsters on your opponent's field with DEF less than or equal to the ATK of 1 face-up "Summoned Skull" or 1 face-up Thunder Type monster on your field. Your monsters cannot attack this turn.

160008059.name: Jurassic Oasis
160008059.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Activate this card by sending the top 2 cards of your Deck to the Graveyard while you have a face-up Dinosaur Type monster on your field.
[EFFECT]
While this card is face-up in the Field Zone, face-up Dinosaur Type monsters on the field cannot be destroyed by monster effects.

160008060.name: Buried Shield
160008060.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
When your opponent Normal Summons a monster, place 1 Field Spell Card from your Graveyard on the bottom of the Deck.
[EFFECT]
Change that monster to face-down Defense Position. Then, you can make 1 face-up Wyrm Type monster on your field gain 500 ATK/DEF until the end of this turn.

160008061.name: Wrath of Light
160008061.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
When your opponent Normal or Special Summons a Level 7 or higher monster face-up while you have a face-up Reptile Type monster on your field.
[EFFECT]
This turn, your opponent's monsters with 3000 or more ATK cannot attack. Also, you can shuffle up to 5 Reptile Type monsters from your Graveyard into the Deck.

160008062.name: Ultimate Fighting Spirit
160008062.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
When an opponent's Level 9 or lower monster declares an attack targeting your Defense Position monster.
[EFFECT]
Negate the attack. Then, change 1 Defense Position monster on your field to face-up Attack Position. Then, if you changed a Normal Monster to face-up Attack Position by this effect, it gains 1000 ATK until the end of this turn.

160008063.name: Sakuretsu Force
160008063.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
When an opponent's monster declares an attack, shuffle 3 monsters from your Graveyard into the Deck.
[EFFECT]
The attacking monster loses 500 ATK until the end of this turn. Then, if you have "Sakuretsu Armor" in your Graveyard, you can destroy up to 2 Attack Position monsters on your opponent's field.

160008064.name: Electrical Discharge
160008064.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
When an opponent's monster declares an attack, shuffle 2 Thunder Type monsters from your Graveyard into the Deck.
[EFFECT]
The attacking monster loses 800 ATK until the end of this turn. Then, inflict 400 damage to your opponent.

160008065.name: Maid's Baneful Gift
160008065.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
When a monster(s) on your field is destroyed by an opponent's attack or their card effect.
[EFFECT]
Draw 2 cards. Then, you can Special Summon 1 "Necromaid Nana" from your Graveyard face-up to your field.

160009000.name: Barrel Dragon (Rush)
160009000.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
None
[EFFECT]
Choose 1 monster on your opponent's field, and toss a coin 3 times. If at least 2 of the results are heads, destroy that monster.

160009001.name: Milky Wave Neo
160009001.description: A new galactic warrior born from the river of stars, the Milky Way. They fight by gathering massive energy from the Stars. Ganary Du Zwai!

160009002.name: Galactica Oblivion
160009002.description: War To Zen! Awesome True Goodnight!

160009003.name: Wooly Wonderland Ground Mouton
160009003.description: The newcomer of the Wooly Wonderland flock. A dyed-in-the-wool slacker.

160009004.name: Wooly Wonderland Pyro Wool
160009004.description: The elder of the Wooly Wonderland flock. It tries to ram through its decisions but the others refuse to be herded.

160009005.name: Wooly Wonderland Night Mutton
160009005.description: The most pensive of the Wooly Wonderland flock. Something of a black sheep, it prefers to stick to its own knitting.

160009006.name: Princess of the Flock - Miss Mutton
160009006.description: Baa-dum, baa-dum, baa-dum, baa-dum, baaaaa-dum! The sheep's in the meadow, the cow's in the corn! You can call me "miss", but I'm actually Wooly Wonderland royalty. I'm never sheepish about chowing on paper (even if it happens to be an important letter).

160009007.name: One Year Broom
160009007.description: A broom with a soul. It's said those who wield this broom work hard to get things done.

160009008.name: Decennium Mystic Sword
160009008.description: A sword with a soul. Those who wield this sword are encouraged to bide their time and wait to make their move.

160009009.name: Centennial Wooden Blade
160009009.description: A wooden sword with a soul. It's said as it's exchanged hands, it's seen people's fortunes wax and wane.

160009010.name: Atlas Combat Beetle
160009010.description: A type of beetle that fights over dark tree sap. It has more power than you can even imagine.

160009011.name: Protector of the Throne (Rush)
160009011.description: While the king is away, this queen protects his throne with a mighty defense.

160009012.name: Griffore (Rush)
160009012.description: This monster's tough hide deflects almost any attack.

160009013.name: Black Handshaker
160009013.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
None
[EFFECT]
Shuffle 1 card from your opponent's Graveyard into the Deck. Then, if you have a face-up Level 7 or higher Normal Monster on your field, you can change 1 Attack Position monster on your opponent's field to face-up Defense Position.

160009014.name: Astro Rescue
160009014.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Your opponent has a monster on their field and you have 2 face-up Normal Monsters on your field.
[EFFECT]
Add 1 Normal Monster from your Graveyard to your hand. This turn, you cannot attack with Level 8 or lower Effect Monsters.

160009015.name: Ozone Layer
160009015.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Send 1 card from your hand to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
This turn, 1 face-up Galaxy Type monster on your field cannot be destroyed by your opponent's Trap Card effects.

160009016.name: Transam Ephyrai
160009016.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
If your opponent has a monster on their field, send the top card of your Deck to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Make 1 face-up "Transam Linac" on your field gain 1000 ATK until the end of this turn.

160009017.name: Satellite Pegasus
160009017.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
During the turn you Normal Summoned this card.
[EFFECT]
Send the top card of your Deck to the Graveyard. Then, if you have 1 or less monsters in your Graveyard, you can destroy 1 face-up Level 8 or lower monster on your opponent's field.

160009018.name: Great Cosmonarch
160009018.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Send 1 card from your hand to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
This card gains 800 ATK until the end of this turn.

160009019.name: Jointech Rex
160009019.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
During the turn you Normal Summoned this card, shuffle 3 monsters from your Graveyard into the Deck.
[EFFECT]
Destroy 1 card in your opponent's Spell & Trap Zone.

160009020.name: Wooly Wonderland Planewe
160009020.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
You have a face-up Beast Type Normal Monster on your field.
[EFFECT]
Set 1 "Meet and Greed" or "Wooly Wonderland - Graveyard Grudge" from your Graveyard to your Spell & Trap Zone. If you have "Princess of the Flock - Miss Mutton" face-up on your field, you can also gain 600 LP.

160009021.name: Poet Fairy
160009021.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
If your opponent has a monster on their field during the turn you Normal Summoned this card, shuffle 3 monsters from your Graveyard into the Deck.
[EFFECT]
Shuffle 3 monsters from your opponent's Graveyard into the Deck. Then, if you have 2 face-up non-Level 1 Spellcaster Type monsters on your field, you can shuffle 3 additional monsters from your opponent's Graveyard into the Deck.

160009022.name: Swordfish Vanguard Gaju
160009022.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
During the turn you Normal Summoned this card.
[EFFECT]
Set 1 "Dolphin Counterattack" or "Seastorm of Iruqua" from your Graveyard in your Spell & Trap Zone. Then, you can Special Summon 1 "Dolphin King Iruqua" from your hand or your Graveyard face-up to your field.

160009023.name: Princess Ladybug White
160009023.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Change this card's battle position (Attack Position becomes face-up Defense Position, Defense Position becomes face-up Attack Position).
[EFFECT]
Special Summon 2 Level 4 or lower Insect Type monsters from your hand face-up to your field. Then, inflict 700 damage to your opponent.

160009024.name: Pakupakuchu
160009024.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
If you have no other monsters on your field, place 1 Beast Type monster from your Graveyard on the bottom of your Deck.
[EFFECT]
Add 1 Beast Type Normal Monster from your Graveyard to your hand.

160009025.name: Swapling Silkworm Fibron
160009025.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
If you have another face-up Insect Type monster on your field, send the top 2 cards of your Deck to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
1 face-up monster on your opponent's field becomes Insect Type this turn.

160009026.name: Therappi
160009026.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Shuffle 2 Reptile Type monsters from your Graveyard into the Deck.
[EFFECT]
Gain 500 LP.

160009027.name: Rapid Carriearth
160009027.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
If your opponent has 3 monsters on their field, shuffle 3 EARTH Attribute Machine Type monsters from your Graveyard into the Deck.
[EFFECT]
Special Summon 1 EARTH Attribute Machine Type monster from your hand face-up to your field. This turn, your Level 6 or lower monsters cannot attack.

160009028.name: Dramoth Caterpillar
160009028.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Send 1 Insect Type monster from your hand to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Draw 1 card.

160009029.name: Shitotsu the Talismanic Warrior
160009029.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
If the only face-up monsters on your field are Warrior Type monsters, place 1 card from your hand on the bottom of the Deck.
[EFFECT]
Special Summon 1 Warrior Type monster with 1000 ATK and 1000 DEF from your Graveyard to your field in face-up Defense Position.

160009030.name: Bio Mechamantis
160009030.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Shuffle 1 Insect Type monster from your Graveyard into the Deck.
[EFFECT]
1 face-up monster on your opponent's field loses 300 ATK until the end of this turn. Then, you can make that monster become Insect Type until the end of this turn.

160009031.name: Crusher Drone
160009031.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
If you have another face-up EARTH Attribute Machine Type monster on your field, send the top 2 cards of your Deck to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
This card gains 400 ATK until the end of this turn.

160009032.name: Ravenous Insect Matiless
160009032.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Send the top card of your Deck to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
1 face-up Insect Type monster on your opponent's field loses 800 ATK/DEF until the end of this turn.

160009033.name: Executie Fermi
160009033.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
If you have a face-up Normal Monster on your field, send the top card of your Deck to the Graveyard.

This card gains 500 ATK until the end of this turn.

160009034.description:

None

160009035.name: Ground Cerberus
160009035.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
None
[EFFECT]
Inflict damage to your opponent equal to [the number of face-up EARTH Attribute Machine Type monsters on your field] x 300.

160009037.description:
"Sevens Road Magician" + "Multistrike Dragon Dragias"

[MULTI-CHOICE EFFECT]

160009041.name: Samurai of the Wooden Sword

"Masaki the Legendary Samurai" + "Centennial Wooden Blade"

[REQUIREMENT]

[EFFECT]

160009042.name: Surge Vortex Dragoon
160009042.description:
"Surge Bolt Lizard" + "Surge Bolt Lizard"

[REQUIREMENT]
Your opponent has a face-up monster on their field.

Add 1 "Electrical Discharge" from your Graveyard to your hand.

160009043.name: Meteor Charge
160009043.description:

None
[EFFECT]
Choose 1 face-up Galaxy Type monster on your field. If it attacks a Defense Position monster this turn, inflict piercing battle damage (if the ATK of the attacking monster exceeds the DEF of the attack target, inflict the difference). Also, if the chosen monster is a Normal Monster, you can change the battle position of 1 monster on your opponent's field (Attack Position becomes face-up Defense Position, Defense Position becomes face-up Attack Position).

160009044.name: Meet and Greed
160009044.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Send 2 cards from your hand to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Choose 1 face-up Beast Type Normal Monster on your field. This turn, that monster can make up to 3 attacks on monsters. If you have "Princess of the Flock - Miss Mutton" face-up on your field, you can also make all face-up Effect Monsters on your opponent's field lose 500 ATK until the end of this turn.

160009045.name: Future Mining
160009045.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Your opponent has 2 or more face-up monsters on their field.
[EFFECT]
Excavate the top 2 cards of your Deck. You can add 1 excavated monster to your hand. Place the remaining cards on the bottom of your Deck in any order.

160009046.name: Sword Skill - Ruler's Slash
160009046.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
If your opponent has a Spell/Trap Card on their field, shuffle 1 Level 8 Warrior Type monster from your Graveyard into the Deck.
[EFFECT]
1 face-up monster with 2500 or more ATK and 2500 or more DEF on your field gains 2500 ATK until the end of this turn. Then, destroy 1 Spell/Trap Card on your opponent's field. This turn, you can only attack with 1 monster.

160009047.name: Defense Destroying Sword
160009047.description:
[REQUIREMENT]

[EFFECT]
Destroy 1 face-up monster with 2000 or more DEF on your opponent's field. Gain 800 LP, and inflict 800 damage to your opponent. This turn, you cannot attack with Effect Monsters.

160009048.name: Telegraphed Strike
160009048.description:

[EFFECT]
Draw 1 card. Then, if you have 2 or more face-up EARTH Attribute Normal Monsters on your field, you can draw 1 additional card.

160009049.name: Sunny Forest
160009049.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
None
[EFFECT]
While this card is face-up in the Field Zone, face-up Defense Position Insect Type monsters on the field cannot be destroyed by card effects.

160009050.name: Insect Rampage
160009050.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Shuffle 2 monsters from your Graveyard into the Deck.
[EFFECT]
All face-up Insect Type monsters on your field gain 300 ATK until the end of this turn. Then, if your opponent has a face-up Insect Type monster on their field, you can destroy 1 face-up Level 8 or lower monster on your opponent's field.

160009051.name: Intruding Beetles
160009051.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
If 2 or more face-up Insect Type monsters are on the field, send 1 card from your hand to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Draw 1 card. Then, you can destroy 1 Spell/Trap Card on your opponent's field.

160009052.name: Executie Up!
160009052.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
None
[EFFECT]
Choose 2 face-up monsters with different Types on your field. This turn, the chosen monsters can be treated as 2 Tributes for the Tribute Summon of a monster in Attack Position. If you have a face-up Level 6 monster with 500 DEF on your field, inflict 800 damage to your opponent.

160009053.name: Ghost Cyclone
160009053.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
You have no monsters on your field.
[EFFECT]
Destroy 1 Spell/Trap Card on your opponent's field. Then, if you have 3 or less monsters in your Graveyard, you can draw 1 card.

160009054.name: Strange Wall
160009054.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
When an opponent's monster declares an attack while you have a Galaxy Type monster in your Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
The attacking monster loses 500 ATK until the end of this turn.

160009055.name: Wooly Wonderland - Graveyard Grudge
160009055.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
When an opponent's monster declares an attack targeting your Attack Position Beast Type Normal Monster, send the top 4 cards of your Deck to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
The attack target loses 2000 ATK until the end of this turn. Then, you can add up to 4 cards sent to the Graveyard to meet the requirement to your hand.

160009056.name: Lucky Mask of Omens
160009056.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
When an opponent's monster declares an attack.
[EFFECT]
1 face-up Warrior Type monster on your field gains ATK equal to [its Level] x 100 until the end of this turn.

160009057.name: Card Reprinting
160009057.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
When an opponent's monster declares an attack.
[EFFECT]
Draw until you have 5 cards in your hand and reveal all cards in your hand. Then, if there is a monster(s) among them, gain LP equal to [the number of those monsters] x 200.

160009058.name: Security Hole
160009058.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
When an opponent's Level 8 or lower monster declares an attack while you have a face-up Level 7 or higher Cyberse Type monster on your field.
[EFFECT]
Shuffle the attacking monster into the Deck.

160009059.name: Demolisher Wyrm Roar
160009059.description:

When your opponent Normal Summons a Level 7 or higher monster while you have a face-up Level 7 or higher Normal Monster on your field.
[EFFECT]
Destroy that Normal Summoned monster.

160009060.name: Climax Clash
160009060.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
When your EARTH Attribute monster is destroyed by an opponent's attack.
[EFFECT]
Inflict damage to your opponent equal to [the number of EARTH Attribute Normal Monsters in your Graveyard] x 100. Then, if you inflicted damage to your opponent by this effect, you can destroy 1 face-up Normal Monster on your opponent's field.

160009061.name: Engage and Strike!
160009061.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
When an opponent's monster declares an attack.
[EFFECT]

160009062.name: Anciant Barrier
160009062.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
When an opponent's Level 8 or lower monster declares an attack, shuffle 2 Insect Type monsters from your Graveyard into the Deck.
[EFFECT]

160009063.name: Ignoring Insect
160009063.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
When your opponent Normal or Special Summons a monster.
[EFFECT]
Change up to 3 Attack Position Insect Type monsters on your field to face-up Defense Position. Then, if you have 2 or more face-up Defense Position monsters on your field, you can change 1 Attack Position monster on your opponent's field to face-up Defense Position.

160009064.name: Hunting Strawberries
160009064.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
When a Spell/Trap Card on your field is destroyed by an opponent's card effect.
[EFFECT]
Destroy 1 face-up monster with 1500 or less ATK on your opponent's field.

160009065.name: Crisis at the Sacred Tower
160009065.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
When your opponent Normal Summons a Level 7 or higher monster.
[EFFECT]
Change 1 face-up Level 8 or lower Effect Monster on your opponent's field to face-down Defense Position.

160010000.name: Abyss Soldier (Rush)
160010000.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Send 1 WATER Attribute monster from your hand to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Return 1 card from the field to the hand.

160010001.name: Wooly Wonderland Aqua Sheep
160010001.description: The most buoyant of the Wooly Wonderland flock. It always remains serene and laid-baaack.

160010002.name: Wooly Wonderland Thunder Rambda
160010002.description: The most lambent of the Wooly Wonderland flock. It conducts the others' activities, always with a twinkle in its eye.

160010003.name: Wooly Wonderland Air Aries
160010003.description: The free-roamer of the Wooly Wonderland flock. It remains blase even while others around are venting.

160010004.name: Hyosube (Rush)
160010004.description: This amphibian is strong on the attack, but leaves much to be desired when defending.

160010005.name: Tutumes Dark Witch
160010005.description: An angelic ballerina who spares no effort. Because of her strong convictions, not even the most intense instruction and practice stops her.

160010006.name: Mean Mutt Blasting Bowwow
160010006.description: A Mean Mutt who fights all his foes with a water pistol. The trust of his allies is... so-so.

160010007.name: Mean Mutt Bullblade
160010007.description: A Mean Mutt who threatens with a throaty deep voice. His ability to intimidate others is... so-so.

160010008.name: Mean Mutt Striking Kai Ken Knuckle
160010008.description: A young Mean Mutt who is extremely motivated, but also pretty reckless. The strength of his grip is... so-so.

160010009.name: Mean Mutt Blaster Chaka Chow Chow
160010009.description: A scary Mean Mutt who usually isn't so scary, until he really gets angry. His determination is... so-so.

160010010.name: Mean Mutt Apex Katana Danbiramatian
160010010.description: The apex of the Mean Mutt who presides over his clumsy so-so subordinates. His proficiency is quite woofderful.

160010011.name: Golden Statue MK-III
160010011.description: Its power source is AA Batteries. Its daily routine is to watch videos while taking a walk. It never works or studies.

160010012.name: Alien 33
160010012.description: A workaholic professional who specializes in the designing and maintenance of spacecraft. He's part of a crazy plan at a certain facility.

160010013.name: Three Warping Witches
160010013.description: A trio of sisters who warp in unique poses. Their hobby is to frighten the operators of spaceships while running alongside them.

160010014.name: Count of the White Dwarf, St. Tremain
160010014.description: A count who has been rumored to live for over 300 years. Immediately after he gets a haircut, he cannot fire his lasers.

160010015.name: Ichtyosterguard
160010015.description: An Ichthyostega soldier with incredible toughness. Since it wears hard and heavy armor, it is quite slow moving.

160010016.name: Nekogal #2 (Rush)
160010016.description: A fast and lethal creature with very dangerous claws.

160010018.name: Nitro Hound
160010018.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
During the turn you Normal Summoned this card.
[EFFECT]
Inflict 400 damage to your opponent. This turn, you can only attack with Pyro Type monsters.

160010019.name: Dynamo Might

[REQUIREMENT]

[EFFECT]
Inflict 300 damage to your opponent.

160010020.name: Chemicalized Salamander

[EFFECT]
All face-up monsters on your opponent's field lose ATK equal to [the number of monsters in your opponent's Graveyard] x 100 until the end of this turn.

160010021.name: Parashroom Colony
160010021.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
You have a face-up Level 7 or higher Galaxy Type monster on your field.
[EFFECT]
Special Summon 1 "Parashroom Colony" from your Graveyard face-up to your field.

160010022.name: Burstray Gunman
160010022.description:
[REQUIREMENT]

[EFFECT]
Inflict damage to your opponent equal to [the number of face-up monsters on their field] x 200. Then, you can make 1 face-up monster on your opponent's field become LIGHT Attribute until the end of this turn.

160010023.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Send this face-up card from your field to the Graveyard.

Special Summon 1 Galaxy Type monster from your hand face-up to your field. Then, if you Special Summoned a Level 8 monster by this effect, this turn, it gains 400 ATK, and if it attacks a Defense Position monster, inflict piercing battle damage (if the ATK of the attacking monster exceeds the DEF of the attack target, inflict the difference).

160010024.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
None

Neither player can Special Summon Level 7 monsters from the Graveyard.

160010025.name: Voidvelg Requiem
160010025.description:
[REQUIREMENT]

[EFFECT]
This card gains ATK equal to [the number of face-up DARK Attribute monsters on your field] x 300 until the end of this turn. Then, if your opponent has a face-up LIGHT Attribute monster on their field, this card gains 600 ATK until the end of this turn.

160010031.name: Mean Mutt Duke Doberguardian

None

160010032.name: Mean Mutt Sacred Shiba

160011051.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Equip this card to 1 face-up monster on your field whose original Type is Psychic.
[EFFECT]
The equipped monster gains 400 ATK. While the equipped monster is face-up on your field, your opponent cannot declare an attack on monsters that are not equipped with an Equip Spell Card.

160011052.name: Heavy Arms - Double Nexcalibur
160011052.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Send 1 WIND Attribute Psychic Type monster from your hand to the Graveyard, and equip this card to 1 face-up Psychic Type monster on your field.
[EFFECT]
The equipped monster can attack twice per turn.

160011053.name: Sacred Arms - Stratosmasher
160011053.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Equip this card to 1 face-up Psychic Type monster on your field.
[EFFECT]
The equipped monster gains 100 ATK and 1500 DEF, also it cannot be destroyed by your opponent's Trap Card effects.

160011054.name: JAM:P Check!
160011054.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
You have 2 or more face-up Psychic Type monsters on your field, including a Normal Monster.
[EFFECT]
Look at up to 2 face-down Spell/Trap Cards on your opponent's field, and destroy 1 of them. Then, if you have "CAN:D" face-up on your field, you can gain 1000 LP.

160011055.name: Music Princess's Prelude
160011055.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
You have no monsters on your field.
[EFFECT]
Special Summon 1 WIND Attribute monster from your hand face-up to your field. Then, if you Special Summoned a Warrior Type monster by this effect, you can add 1 "Fusion" from your Graveyard to your hand.

160011056.name: Atrium's Wind
160011056.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Send 1 WIND Attribute monster from your hand to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Draw 1 card. Then, if you have 2 or more face-up WIND Attribute monsters with 1800 or more ATK on your field, you can draw 1 additional card.

160011057.name: Descent of the Sweeping Spirit
160011057.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Reveal 2 Fairy Type monsters in your hand.
[EFFECT]
Special Summon 1 Level 7 or higher Fairy Type monster from your Graveyard face-up to your field. Then, if you Special Summoned a monster other than "Arzareth the Sweeping Wind" by this effect, send 2 monsters from your hand to the Graveyard.

160011058.name: Beast Swords - Tiger Sabre
160011058.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Equip this card to 1 face-up Normal Monster with 1400 or less ATK on your field.
[EFFECT]
The equipped monster gains 900 ATK. The equipped monster can be treated as 2 Tributes for the Tribute Summon of a monster in Attack Position.

160011059.name: Equipment of Ascension
160011059.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Equip this card to 1 face-up monster on your field.
[EFFECT]
Increase the Level of the equipped monster by 2 and its ATK/DEF by 200.

160011060.name: Site Preview
160011060.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
After your opponent activates a Spell Card.
[EFFECT]
Add 1 Level 4 or lower monster from your Graveyard to your hand.

160011061.name: Indigo Prison
160011061.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
When your opponent Normal or Special Summons a monster, send 1 monster from your field to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
This turn, neither player can Special Summon Level 7 or 8 monsters from the Graveyard.

160011062.name: Slash Halo
160011062.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
When an opponent's monster declares an attack targeting your Attack Position Fairy Type monster, pay 500 LP.
[EFFECT]
The attacking monster loses 1000 ATK until the end of this turn.

160011063.name: Back Jersey
160011063.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
When your opponent Normal or Special Summons a Level 5 or higher monster face-up, pay 500 LP.
[EFFECT]
1 face-up monster with 500 DEF on your field gains 500 ATK until the end of this turn. Then, you can shuffle up to 5 monsters from your opponent's Graveyard into the Deck.

160011064.name: Looter Force
160011064.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
When a card in your Spell & Trap Zone is destroyed by an opponent's card effect.
[EFFECT]
Set up to 2 Spell/Trap Cards from your Graveyard in your Spell & Trap Zone. Then, you can choose up to 3 face-up Level 7 or higher Psychic Type monsters on your field. If you do, those monsters cannot be destroyed by battle this turn.

160011065.name: Revenge MAX
160011065.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
When your opponent Normal or Special Summons a monster face-up.
[EFFECT]
Destroy 1 Spell/Trap Card on your field. Then, if you destroyed an Equip Spell Card by this effect, you can destroy 1 of those Normal or Special Summoned Level 8 or lower monsters.

160012000.name: Gilford the Lightning (Rush)
160012000.description:
You can Tribute Summon this card in Attack Position by Tributing 3 monsters.

[REQUIREMENT]
During the turn you Normal Summoned this card by Tributing 3 monsters.
[EFFECT]
Destroy all monsters on your opponent's field.

160012001.name: Chromatographagas
160012001.description: This flesh may burneth and vaporize... but as long as mine own fighting spirit remains unextinguished, mine own corse shall beest immortal.

160012002.name: Ray Dragon
160012002.description: A dragon that lives in cold territories. It moves at high speeds through snowy paths.

160012003.name: The Dragias
160012003.description: A dragon that made seven supernovae go gamma-ray burst. Its name is... The Dragias! The Dragias!!

160012004.name: Silver-Eyes Star Cat
160012004.description: A star cat with eyes of silver. They're filled with wonder.

160012005.name: Golden-Eyes Star Cat
160012005.description: A star cat with eyes of gold. They're filled with charm.

160012006.name: Jointech Tinosaurus
160012006.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Send 1 card from your hand to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Change 1 Attack Position monster on your opponent's field to face-up Defense Position. Then, that monster loses 2000 DEF until the end of this turn.

160012007.name: Red Riser
160012007.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
During the turn you Normal Summoned this card.
[EFFECT]
Add 1 "Chemicalizer Red" from your Graveyard to your hand.

160012008.name: Voidvelg Kataphraktos
160012008.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
You Normal Summoned this card this turn and have another face-up DARK Attribute monster on your field.
[EFFECT]
Send the top card of your Deck to the Graveyard. Then, if you sent a monster to the Graveyard by this effect, you can add 1 Level 8 Galaxy Type monster from your Graveyard to your hand.

160012009.name: Voidvelg Black Dwarf
160012009.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
During the turn you Normal Summoned this card.
[EFFECT]
Special Summon 1 Level 4 DARK Attribute Galaxy Type Normal Monster from your Graveyard face-up to your field.

160012010.name: Machvio of the Ultimate Aria
160012010.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
None
[CONTINUOUS EFFECT]
This card gains ATK equal to [the total number of Equip Spell Cards equipped to this card and the number of face-up Normal Monsters on your opponent's field] x 500.

160012011.name: Double-Doom Dragon
160012011.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Send the top 2 cards of your Deck to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Gain 200 LP. Then, you can Set 1 "Dragon Double-Doom" from your Graveyard in your Spell & Trap Zone.

160012012.name: The Clone
160012012.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
If the only monsters in your Graveyard are High Dragon and/or Dragon Type monsters, send 1 card from your hand to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Draw 1 card. Then, if you have "The Copy" or "Back To The Fusion" in your Graveyard, this card's name becomes "The Dragias" this turn.

160012013.name: Mirroring Wyvern
160012013.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
If the only monsters in your Graveyard are High Dragon and/or Dragon Type monsters during the turn you Normal Summoned this card.
[EFFECT]
Special Summon 1 Normal Monster from your Graveyard face-up to your field. Then, this turn, this card's name becomes the same as the name of the monster Special Summoned by this effect.

160012014.name: Purple-Eyes Star Cat
160012014.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
None
[EFFECT]
Set 1 "Stray Force" from your Graveyard in your Spell & Trap Zone. Then, you can choose 1 face-up Level 7 or higher monster with 200 DEF on your field. If you do, that monster can attack twice during this turn.

160012015.name: Green-Eyes Star Cat
160012015.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Send 1 Beast or Warrior Type monster with 200 DEF from your hand to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Draw 1 card. Also, if you sent a Normal Monster to the Graveyard to meet the requirement, this face-up card can be treated as 2 Tributes for the Tribute Summon of a monster with 200 DEF in Attack Position this turn.

160012016.name: Cat Claw Girl
160012016.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Place 1 card from your hand on the bottom of the Deck.
[EFFECT]
Special Summon 1 Beast Type monster with 200 DEF from your Graveyard face-up to your field. Then, if you Special Summoned a Normal Monster by this effect, you can Set 1 "Fusion" from your Graveyard in your Spell & Trap Zone.

160012017.name: Dark-Eyes Breakstar Cat
160012017.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Send the top 2 cards of your Deck to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
If this card attacks a Defense Position monster this turn, inflict piercing battle damage (if the ATK of the attacking monster exceeds the DEF of the attack target, inflict the difference). Also, if you activated this effect during your Main Phase this card was Special Summoned, you can destroy 1 face-up Level 7 or 8 monster on your opponent's field.

160012018.name: Cyber Coatl
160012018.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
You have no other monsters on your field.
[EFFECT]
Excavate the top 3 cards of your Deck. You can Special Summon 1 excavated Level 5 Machine Type monster face-up to your field. Place the remaining cards on the bottom of your Deck in any order.

160012019.name: Executie Flame
160012019.description:
If your opponent has a face-up Level 6 or higher monster on their field, you can Special Summon this card from your hand face-up to your field.

[REQUIREMENT]
Send 1 card from your hand to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
This card gains ATK equal to [the number of face-up Level 6 or higher monsters on the field] x 600 until the end of this turn. This turn, you can only attack with this card.

160012020.name: Soleil the Skysavior Angel
160012020.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Reveal 1 Warrior Type monster in your hand.
[EFFECT]
This card's name becomes "Lua the Skysavior Angel" this turn. Then, excavate the top 4 cards of your Deck. You can add 1 excavated "Fusion" to your hand. Place the remaining cards on the bottom of the Deck in any order.

160012021.name: Lua the Skysavior Angel
160012021.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Reveal 1 Warrior Type monster in your hand:
[EFFECT]
This card's name becomes "Soleil the Skysavior Angel" this turn. Then, send the top 3 cards of your Deck to the Graveyard. Then, you can add 1 "Fusion" from among the cards sent to the Graveyard by this effect to your hand.

160012022.name: Ranga the Skysavior Knight
160012022.description:

[EFFECT]

160012023.name: Seir the Skysavior Knight

160012024.name: Ciela the Skysavior Knight

160012025.name: Dunkes the Skysavior Knight
160012025.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Reveal up to 5 Celestial Warrior Type monsters with different names in your Extra Deck.
[EFFECT]
This card gains ATK equal to [the number of monsters revealed to meet the requirement] x 200 until the end of this turn. This turn, this card cannot attack directly, and you can only attack with Celestial Warrior, Warrior, or Fairy Type monsters.

160012026.name: Astrobio Drake
160012026.description:

160012027.name: Engine Reviver

[EFFECT]

160012028.name: Gilford the Rising

[EFFECT]

[EFFECT]

160012031.name: Melel the Beautiful Flame Spirit of the Lamp

[REQUIREMENT]
None
[EFFECT]

[REQUIREMENT]

[EFFECT]
Destroy all Spell/Trap Cards on the field. Then, you can make all face-up monsters on your opponent's field lose ATK equal to [the number of Spell Cards destroyed by this effect] x 1000 until the end of this turn.

None

[REQUIREMENT]
If the only monsters in your Graveyard are Dragon and/or High Dragon Type monsters, pay 500 LP.

● 1 face-up Normal Monster on your field can attack twice this turn.
● Set 1 "Fusion" from your Graveyard in your Spell & Trap Zone.

160012035.name: The Dragiastar
160012035.description:
"The Dragias" + "The Dragias"

[REQUIREMENT]
If you have 2 or more Normal Monsters with the same name in your Graveyard, send 1 card from your hand to the Graveyard.
[MULTI-CHOICE EFFECT]
● 2 Attack Position monsters with the same name on your field can attack twice this turn.
● Special Summon 2 Normal Monsters with the same name from your Graveyard face-up to your field.

160012036.name: Star Cat Straynya
160012036.description:
"Cat Claw Girl" + "Silver-Eyes Star Cat"

[EFFECT]
1 face-up monster on your opponent's field loses 2200 ATK/DEF until the end of this turn. Then, if you sent a Normal Monster with 200 original DEF to the Graveyard to meet the requirement, you can destroy 1 Spell/Trap Card on your opponent's field.

160012037.name: Star Cat Destronya
160012037.description:
"Cat Claw Girl" + "Golden-Eyes Star Cat"

[REQUIREMENT]
Shuffle 2 monsters with 200 DEF from your Graveyard into the Deck.
[EFFECT]
Special Summon 2 monsters with 200 DEF and the same Level from your Graveyard face-up to your field. If you Special Summoned Normal Monsters by this effect, those Normal Monsters gain 2200 ATK until the end of this turn.

160012038.name: Solcier the Skysavior Lightflash
160012038.description:
"Ciela the Skysavior Knight" + "Soleil the Skysavior Angel"

[REQUIREMENT]
Place 1 other card from your field on the bottom of the owner's Deck.
[MULTI-CHOICE EFFECT]
● Destroy Spell/Trap Cards on your opponent's field, up to [the number of face-up Celestial Warrior Type monsters on your field].
● Add 1 "Skysavior Symbol" from your Graveyard to your hand.

160012039.name: Altierra the Skysavior Transience
160012039.description:
"Ciela the Skysavior Knight" + "Lua the Skysavior Angel"

[REQUIREMENT]
None
[CONTINUOUS EFFECT]
Your opponent cannot activate Normal Spell Cards, except "Fusion".

160012040.name: Digrace the Skysavior Radiance
160012040.description:
"Dunkes the Skysavior Knight" + "Soleil the Skysavior Angel"

[REQUIREMENT]
Send the top card of your Deck to the Graveyard.
[MULTI-CHOICE EFFECT]
● This card gains ATK equal to [the number of face-up Celestial Warrior Type monsters on your field] x 1000 until the end of this turn.
● This turn, this card can make up to 2 attacks on monsters.

160012041.name: Drukmoor the Skysavior Phantom
160012041.description:
"Dunkes the Skysavior Knight" + "Lua the Skysavior Angel"

[REQUIREMENT]
None
[CONTINUOUS EFFECT]
Face-up cards on your field cannot be destroyed by your opponent's card effects.

160012042.name: Stealthagic

[REQUIREMENT]
Send 1 card from your hand to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Draw 1 card. Then, if you sent a Spell Card to the Graveyard to meet the requirement and your LP are 1000 or lower, draw 1 additional card.

160012043.name: Cracking Claw
160012043.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Equip this card to 1 face-up Dragon Type monster on your field.
[EFFECT]
The equipped monster gains ATK equal to [the number of face-up Dragon Type monsters on the field] x 200. When the equipped monster attacks a Level 7 or higher Defense Position monster, inflict piercing battle damage (if the ATK of the attacking monster exceeds the DEF of the attack target, inflict the difference).

160012044.name: Voidvelg Phalanx
160012044.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Equip this card to 1 face-up Galaxy Type monster on your field.
[EFFECT]
The equipped monster gains 200 ATK/DEF. If the equipped monster is DARK Attribute, it cannot be destroyed by your opponent's Trap Card effects, and if it attacks a Defense Position monster, inflict piercing battle damage (if the ATK of the attacking monster exceeds the DEF of the attack target, inflict the difference).

160012045.name: Road Arms - Sword Breaker
160012045.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
If you have no other face-up "Road Arms - Sword Breaker" on your field, equip this card to 1 face-up "Sevens Road Magician" on your field.
[EFFECT]
The equipped monster gains ATK equal to [the number of equipped Equip Spell Cards on the field] x 1000 and cannot be destroyed by your opponent's Trap Card effects.

160012046.name: The Copy
160012046.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Your opponent has a face-up Level 7 or higher monster on their field.
[EFFECT]
Special Summon 1 Normal Monster with the same name as a face-up monster on your field, from your Graveyard face-up to your field.

160012047.name: Back to The Fusion
160012047.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
You have 2 or more face-up monsters with the same name on your field.
[EFFECT]
Add 1 "Fusion" from your Graveyard to your hand. Then, if you have 2 or more Normal Monsters with the same name in your Graveyard, you can add 1 of them to your hand.

160012048.name: Vice Slasher
160012048.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
If you have 2 or more face-up Dragon Type Normal Monsters with the same name on your field, equip this card to 1 of them.
[EFFECT]
The equipped monster gains ATK equal to [its original ATK]. The equipped monster cannot attack directly.

160012049.name: Nyanderful Rush
160012049.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Place 1 card from your hand on the bottom of the Deck.
[EFFECT]
Special Summon up to 2 Beast and/or Warrior Type monsters with 200 DEF from your Graveyard to your field in face-up Defense Position. This turn, you can only attack with monsters with 200 DEF.

160012050.name: Rising Luna Radiant Luster
160012050.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
If you have a Celestial Warrior Type Fusion Monster or "Kimeluna the Dark Shifter" face-up on your field, send 1 card from your hand to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Destroy 1 card on your opponent's field.

160012051.name: Blaze Fiend Assault
160012051.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Send 3 FIRE Attribute Maximum Monsters from your hand to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Shuffle all face-up monsters on your opponent's field into the owner's Deck. Then, you can make 1 face-up Maximum Monster on your field gain 1000 ATK until the end of this turn.

160012052.name: Skysavior Prayer
160012052.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Send 1 card from your hand to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Special Summon 1 LIGHT or DARK Attribute Celestial Warrior Type monster from your Graveyard face-up to your field.

160012053.name: Skysavior Watch
160012053.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Reveal 2 Warrior and/or Fairy Type monsters in your hand.
[EFFECT]
Excavate the top 5 cards of your Deck. Add 1 excavated card to your hand. Then, place the remaining cards on the bottom of your Deck in any order. This turn, your Level 8 or lower monsters cannot attack, and your opponent takes no effect damage.

160012054.name: Skysavior Symbol
160012054.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
If your opponent has a face-up monster on their field, equip this card to 1 face-up Celestial Warrior, Warrior, or Fairy Type monster on your field.
[EFFECT]
The equipped monster gains ATK equal to [its Level] x 100.

160012055.name: Ring of Storms
160012055.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Shuffle 2 monsters from your Graveyard into the Deck.
[EFFECT]
Shuffle 2-7 monsters with different names from your opponent's Graveyard into their Deck. Then, if you shuffled 6 or more monsters by this effect, you can shuffle 1 face-up Level 8 or lower monster from your opponent's field into the owner's Deck.

160012056.name: Transam Lightning
160012056.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
When an opponent's monster declares an attack targeting your face-up Level 4 or lower Galaxy Type Normal Monster.
[EFFECT]
The attack target cannot be destroyed by battle this turn.

160012057.name: Jointech Great Wall
160012057.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
When your opponent Normal or Special Summons a Level 7 or higher monster face-up while you have a face-up Level 7 or higher EARTH Attribute Machine Type monster on your field.
[EFFECT]
This turn, up to 3 face-up EARTH Attribute Machine Type monsters on your field gain 300 ATK and cannot be destroyed by battle.

160012058.name: Tribute Block
160012058.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
When your opponent Normal Summons a Level 5 or higher monster.
[EFFECT]
Change that Normal Summoned monster and 1 Attack Position Dragon or Machine Type monster on your field to face-up Defense Position.

160012059.name: Dark Nebula
160012059.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
When your DARK Attribute Galaxy Type monster with 1500 or more ATK is destroyed by an opponent's attack.
[EFFECT]
Special Summon 1 DARK Attribute Galaxy Type monster from your Graveyard to your field in face-up Attack Position. The monster Special Summoned by this effect loses 500 ATK until the end of this turn.

160012060.name: Dragon Double-Doom
160012060.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
When an opponent's monster declares an attack while you have a face-up High Dragon or Dragon Type monster on your field.
[EFFECT]
You choose which of your monsters becomes the attack target for your opponent's attack. Then, if you have 2 or more face-up monsters with the same name on your field, you can destroy 1 monster on your opponent's field.

160012061.name: Stray Force
160012061.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
When an opponent's monster declares an attack.
[EFFECT]
The attacking monster loses 200 ATK until the end of this turn. Then, if you have 3 face-up Beast, Beast-Warrior, and/or Warrior Type monsters with 200 DEF on your field, you can destroy all Attack Position monsters on your opponent's field.

160012062.name: Ether Escape
160012062.description:

When your opponent Normal Summons a Level 7 or higher monster, shuffle 2 Warrior and/or Machine Type monsters from your Graveyard into the Deck.
[EFFECT]
Change that Normal Summoned monster to face-down Defense Position. Then, if you have a face-up Fusion Monster on your field, you can place 1 face-down card from your opponent's field on top of the owner's Deck.

160012063.name: Traditional Tax
160012063.description:

[EFFECT]
Send 2 random cards from your opponent's hand to the Graveyard.

160012064.name: Buffered Slime

[REQUIREMENT]
When an opponent's Level 8 or lower monster declares an attack.
[EFFECT]
Send the top card of your Deck to the Graveyard. This turn, you take no battle damage. Also, if your LP are 3000 or more, take 2000 damage.

160012065.name: Phantom Roar
160012065.description:
