When your monster is destroyed by an opponent's attack, shuffle 2 Level 5 or higher monsters from your Graveyard into the Deck.
[EFFECT]
Destroy 1 face-up Level 8 or lower monster on your opponent's field. Then, you can make 1 face-up monster on your opponent's field lose 1000 ATK until the end of your next turn.

160012066.name: Multistrike Dragon Dragias
160012066.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Send the top card of your Deck to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
This turn, if this card destroyed a monster by battle, it can make a second attack during that Battle Phase.

160013000.name: Sevens Road Witch
160013000.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Send 1 card from your hand to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Special Summon 1 Level 7 or higher, DARK Attribute, Spellcaster Type monster from your hand, face-up to your field. If you Special Summoned "Sevens Road Magician" by this effect, this card gains 400 ATK until the end of this turn.

160013001.name: Earth Sorcerer
160013001.description: A magician who carries the pride of his family in his heart. On that day, he left his hometown as if he were on the run.

160013002.name: Aero Sorcerer
160013002.description: A magician who enjoys being as free as the wind blows. His selfish behavior will eventually bind his future.

160013003.name: Galactica Deja Vu
160013003.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
If your opponent's LP are 4000 or higher, send this face-up card from your field to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Send the top card of your Deck to the Graveyard. Then, if you sent a Level 4 or lower LIGHT Attribute Galaxy Type Normal Monster to the Graveyard by this effect, you can Special Summon that monster face-up to your field. Then, inflict damage to your opponent equal to [the original ATK of the monster Special Summoned by this effect].

160013004.name: Booster Wyvern
160013004.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
You have "Blue-Fang Burst Dragon" or "Red-Boot Boost Dragon" face-up on your field during your Main Phase that you Normal or Special Summoned this card.
[EFFECT]
Inflict 600 damage to your opponent.

160013005.name: DBF Rebuildra
160013005.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
During your Main Phase that you Normal or Special Summoned this card, reveal 1 "Blue-Fang Burst Dragon" or "Red-Boot Boost Dragon" in your hand.
[EFFECT]
Set 1 "Dragons Burst Fusion" or "Dragons Boost Fusion" from your Graveyard to your Spell & Trap Zone.

160013006.name: Voidvelg Kyrie
160013006.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Send 1 face-up Level 7 or lower Galaxy Type monster from your field to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Add 1 "Voidvelg Requiem" or "Voidvelg Chrysaor" from your Graveyard to your hand. Then, you can choose 1 face-up card on your field. If you do, that card cannot be destroyed by card effects this turn.

160013007.name: Voidvelg Logistikos
160013007.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Reveal 1 Level 7 or higher Galaxy Type monster in your hand.
[EFFECT]
Set 1 "Fusion" from your Graveyard in your Spell & Trap Zone. Then, if your opponent has a face-up Level 7 or higher monster on their field, you can add 1 Level 8 Galaxy Type monster from your Graveyard to your hand.

160013008.name: Voidvelg Chrysaor
160013008.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Your opponent has 2 or more monsters on their field.
[EFFECT]
Send the top 3 cards of your Deck to the Graveyard. If a DARK Attribute Galaxy Type monster(s) is among the cards sent, this card can attack up to that many times this turn. Also, if the cards sent are 3 DARK Attribute Galaxy Type monsters with the same Level, you can destroy all face-up Level 8 or lower monsters on your opponent's field.

160013009.name: Celeb Rose Mage
160013009.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
You have "Celeb Rose Magician" or an Equip Spell Card in your Graveyard during the turn you Normal Summoned this card.
[EFFECT]
Add 1 "Charis Magic Scepter - Death Wand" or "Fusion" from your Graveyard to your hand.

160013010.name: Celeb Rose Sorcerer
160013010.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Send 3 face-up LIGHT Attribute Spellcaster Type monsters from your field to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Special Summon 1 LIGHT Attribute Spellcaster Type monster with 2500 or less ATK from your Graveyard face-up to your field. Then, you can Set 1 "Charis Magic Scepter - Death Wand" from your Graveyard in your Spell & Trap Zone.

160013011.name: Celeb Rose Witch
160013011.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
If you have "Celeb Rose Magician" in your Graveyard, send 1 LIGHT Attribute Spellcaster Type monster or 1 Spell Card from your hand to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Special Summon 1 "Celeb Rose Magician" or 1 Level 9 or lower Spellcaster Type Fusion Monster from your Graveyard face-up to your field.

160013012.name: Celeb Rose Magician
160013012.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Send 1 face-up Equip Spell Card from your field to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Destroy 1 face-up Level 8 or lower monster on your opponent's field. Then, if you have 3 or more Spell Cards in your Graveyard, this card gains 700 ATK until the end of this turn.

160013013.name: Magiarms Beast Gearpard
160013013.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
None
[CONTINUOUS EFFECT]
If a card is in your Spell & Trap Zone, this card gains 200 ATK, also this Attack Position card cannot be destroyed by battle during your opponent's turn.

160013014.name: Zuse the Wisdom Vassal
160013014.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
During the turn you Normal Summoned this card, shuffle 2 monsters with 1000 DEF from your Graveyard into the Deck.
[EFFECT]
Your opponent Sets 1 Spell Card from their Graveyard to their field. Then, you can add 1 Level 5 or higher monster with 1000 DEF from your Graveyard to your hand.

160013015.name: Hebe the Star Vassal
160013015.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
During the turn you Normal Summoned this card, shuffle 2 monsters with 1000 DEF from your Graveyard into the Deck.
[EFFECT]
Your opponent Special Summons 1 Level 6 or lower Effect Monster from their Graveyard to their field in face-up Defense Position. Then, you can add 1 Level 5 or higher monster with 1000 DEF from your Graveyard to your hand.

160013016.name: Wilhel the Wisdom Monarch
160013016.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
During the turn you Tribute Summoned this card in Attack Position.
[EFFECT]
Look at 1 face-down Spell/Trap Card on your opponent's field. Then, if that card is a Spell Card, you can destroy it.

160013017.name: Estrome the Star Monarch
160013017.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
During the turn you Tribute Summoned this card in Attack Position.
[EFFECT]
Destroy 1 face-up Level 6 or lower Effect Monster on your opponent's field.

160013018.name: Wilhel the Mega Monarch
160013018.description:
You can Tribute Summon this card in Attack Position by Tributing 1 face-up Level 5 or higher monster with 1000 DEF.

[REQUIREMENT]
During the turn you Tribute Summoned this card in Attack Position.
[EFFECT]
Your opponent chooses 1 card on their field, and you destroy that card.

160013019.name: Estrome the Mega Monarch
160013019.description:
You can Tribute Summon this card in Attack Position by Tributing 1 face-up Level 5 or higher monster with 1000 DEF.

[REQUIREMENT]
During the turn you Tribute Summoned this card in Attack Position.
[EFFECT]
Your opponent chooses 1 card on their field, and you destroy 1 other card on either field.

160013020.name: Zaborg the Thunder Monarch (Rush)
160013020.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
During the turn you Tribute Summoned this card in Attack Position.
[EFFECT]
Destroy 1 monster on either field.

160013021.name: Cyber Processor
160013021.description:
If you have a face-up Machine Type monster on your field, you can Special Summon this card from your hand face-up to your field.

[REQUIREMENT]
Send 1 other card from your field to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
This card's name becomes "Cyber Dragon" this turn. Then, you can Special Summon 1 "Cyber Dragon" from your Graveyard face-up to your field.

160013022.name: Star Replacer
160013022.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
If you have no other monsters on your field, return this card from your field to the owner's hand.
[EFFECT]
Special Summon 1 Level 4 or lower monster from your Graveyard to your field in face-down Defense Position. For the rest of this turn, you cannot Special Summon monsters from your hand or Graveyard.

160013023.name: Don A. Corn of the Verdant Vast
160013023.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Send 3 Spell/Trap Cards from your field to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Destroy 1 monster on your opponent's field.

160013024.name: Braid Blade Reader
160013024.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Send 1 LIGHT Attribute Spellcaster Type monster or 1 Spell Card from your hand to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Send the top 3 cards of your Deck to the Graveyard. If a LIGHT Attribute Spellcaster Type monster(s) is among the cards sent, you can add 1 Equip Spell Card from your Graveyard to your hand.

160013025.name: Skyporter Max
160013025.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Shuffle 10 monsters from your Graveyard into the Deck.
[EFFECT]
Place 2 or 3 Maximum Monsters from your Graveyard on top of the Deck in any order.

160013026.name: Devil Foolish
160013026.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
During the turn you Normal Summoned this card, reveal up to 2 monsters with 0 DEF in your hand.
[EFFECT]
Special Summon monsters with 0 DEF from your Graveyard, up to [the number of monsters revealed to meet the requirement], to your field in face-down Defense Position. For the rest of this turn, you cannot Normal Summon Level 9 or lower monsters nor Set monsters from the hand.

160013027.name: Splame
160013027.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Shuffle 2 Pyro Type monsters from your Graveyard into the Deck.
[EFFECT]
This turn, this card's name becomes the same as the name of 1 Level 8 or lower monster in your Graveyard.

160013028.name: Elegant Aurum Avian
160013028.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
If you have 10 or more cards in your Deck, send 1 LIGHT Attribute Spellcaster Type monster from your hand to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Draw 1 card.

160013029.name: Plaster Scout
160013029.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
None
[CONTINUOUS EFFECT]
During your opponent's Main Phase, you take no damage from your opponent's card effects.

160013030.name: Mad Rare Aquila
160013030.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
If your opponent has 2 or more monsters on their field, send the top card of your Deck to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
This turn, this card can attack twice. Also, you can destroy 1 face-up Level 6 Effect Monster on your opponent's field. Then, if you destroyed a monster by this effect, this card gains 600 ATK until the end of this turn.

160013031.name: Extra Plorer
160013031.description:
[REQUIREMENT]

[EFFECT]

160013032.name: Summoning Sorcerer Doretheo
160013032.description:

None

"Galactiara Eve" + 1 LIGHT Attribute Galaxy Type monster

[REQUIREMENT]

[EFFECT]
Draw 1 card. Then, you can Special Summon 1 Galaxy Type Normal Monster from your Graveyard face-up to your field.

"Galactica Oblivion" + 2 LIGHT Attribute Galaxy Type monsters

[REQUIREMENT]

[EFFECT]
Send the top 3 cards of your Deck to the Graveyard. This turn, this card cannot be destroyed by your opponent's Trap Card effects. Then, you can make this card gain ATK equal to [the number of monsters in your Graveyard] x 300 until the end of this turn.

160013036.name: Tamabot Burst Dragon
160013036.description:
"Blue-Fang Burst Dragon" + "Tamabot"
[REQUIREMENT]
Send cards from the top of your Deck to the Graveyard equal to [the total number of "Tamabot" in both players' Graveyards].
[EFFECT]
This card gains 1000 ATK until the end of this turn. Then, if you sent a monster with 1500 or less ATK to the Graveyard to meet the requirement, you can destroy 1 face-up monster with 1500 or more ATK on your opponent's field.

160013037.name: Blue-Fang Enhanced Burst Dragon
160013037.description:
"Blue-Fang Burst Dragon" + "Booster Wyvern"
[REQUIREMENT]
Send 1 monster from your field to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Destroy 1 face-up card on the field. Then, if you sent a monster whose original Level is 7 or higher to the Graveyard to meet the requirement, you can Special Summon 1 "Blue-Fang Burst Dragon" from your Graveyard face-up to your field.

160013038.name: Red-Boot Enhanced Boost Dragon
160013038.description:
"Red-Boot Boost Dragon" + "Booster Wyvern"

[REQUIREMENT]
None
[EFFECT]
Choose up to 9 monsters in any Graveyard(s). Inflict damage to your opponent equal to [the number of chosen monsters] x 200, and this card gains ATK equal to [the number of chosen monsters] x 200 until the end of this turn. Then, shuffle the chosen monsters into the owner's Deck.

160013039.name: Voidvelg Theogonia
160013039.description:
"Voidvelg Chrysaor" + "Dark Prophet"

[REQUIREMENT]
During your Main Phase this card was Special Summoned.
[EFFECT]
Special Summon 1 Level 8 Galaxy Type monster from your Graveyard face-up to your field. The monster Special Summoned by this effect cannot be destroyed by card effects until the end of your opponent's next turn.

160013040.name: Voidvelg Gigantomachia

"Voidvelg Requiem" + "Voidvelg Chrysaor"

[REQUIREMENT]
Send 1 card from your hand to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Destroy 1 Spell/Trap Card on the field. Then, this turn, this card gains 500 ATK, and can attack twice.

160013041.name: Celeb Rose Fabulous Magician

"Celeb Rose Magician" + "Celeb Rose Witch"

[REQUIREMENT]
Send 1 card from your hand to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Destroy 1 face-up monster on your opponent's field. Then, you can add 1 Equip Spell Card from your Graveyard to your hand.

160013042.name: Celeb Rose Luxury Magicians
160013042.description:
"Celeb Rose Magician" + "Celeb Rose Witch"

[REQUIREMENT]
None
[EFFECT]
Special Summon 1 Level 9 or lower LIGHT Attribute Spellcaster Type monster from your Graveyard to your field in face-up Defense Position. Then, if this card is equipped with an Equip Spell Card, this card can make up to 2 attacks on monsters this turn.

160013043.name: Sevens Chariot the Magical Knight
160013043.description:
"Sevens Road Magician" + "Magiarms Beast Gearpard"

[REQUIREMENT]
Send the top card of your Deck to the Graveyard.
[MULTI-CHOICE EFFECT]
● This card gains ATK equal to [the number of cards in both players' Spell & Trap Zones] x 500 until the end of this turn.
● This turn, this card cannot be destroyed by your opponent's card effects. Also, you can destroy face-up cards on your opponent's field, up to [the number of cards in your Spell & Trap Zone].

160013044.name: Cyber Tactical Dragon
160013044.description:
"Cyber Assault Dragon" + "Cyber Dragon"

[REQUIREMENT]
Shuffle 2 LIGHT Attribute Machine Type monsters from your Graveyard into the Deck.
[EFFECT]
Destroy up to 2 face-up monsters on your opponent's field, whose total ATK is less than or equal to this card's.

160013045.name: Space Fusion - Extra Plasma
160013045.description:
"Extra Plorer" + 1 LIGHT Attribute Galaxy Type monster
[REQUIREMENT]
Send the top 2 cards of your Deck to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Destroy 1 Spell/Trap Card on your opponent's field.

160013047.name: Galactica Adargatling
160013047.description:

[EFFECT]

None

160013049.name: Dragons Boost Fusion
160013049.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
None
[EFFECT]

Then, if you sent "Red-Boot Boost Dragon" to the Graveyard by this effect, you can send the top 7 cards of your Deck to the Graveyard. Then, if you sent a card from the Deck to the Graveyard, you can send the top 7 cards of your opponent's Deck to the Graveyard.

160013050.name: Voidvelg Gullinbursti
160013050.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Equip this card to 1 face-up DARK Attribute Galaxy Type monster on your field.
[EFFECT]
The equipped monster cannot be destroyed by Spell Card effects, also it gains 800 ATK during your turn.

160013051.name: Voidvelg Shroud
160013051.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Equip this card to 1 face-up Galaxy Type monster on your field.
[EFFECT]
The equipped monster gains ATK equal to [the number of Spell/Trap Cards on your field] x 100. While the equipped monster is face-up on your field, Spell/Trap Cards on your field cannot be destroyed by your opponent's card effects.

160013052.description:

Send 1 LIGHT Attribute Spellcaster Type monster or 1 Equip Spell Card from your hand to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Draw 1 card. Then, if you have 4 or more monsters in your Graveyard, draw 1 additional card.

160013053.name: Charis Magic Scepter - Death Wand
160013053.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Equip this card to 1 face-up LIGHT Attribute Spellcaster Type monster on your field.
[EFFECT]
The equipped monster gains 400 ATK and cannot be destroyed by your opponent's card effects. If the equipped monster is a Fusion Monster, it gains 600 more ATK.

160013054.name: Sevens Wonder Fusion

None
[EFFECT]
Fusion Summon by shuffling monsters from your field or Graveyard into the owner's Deck as material, including "Sevens Road Magician".

160013055.name: Magical Lance - Grace Spear

Equip this card to 1 face-up Magical Knight or Spellcaster Type monster on your field.

The equipped monster gains 200 ATK, and if it attacks a Defense Position monster, inflict piercing battle damage (if the ATK of the attacking monster exceeds the DEF of the attack target, inflict the difference). If the equipped monster is Magical Knight Type, it gains additional ATK equal to [its Level] x 200.

The equipped monster cannot be destroyed by your opponent's card effects. Also, if you have an Equip Spell Card in your Graveyard, the equipped monster gains 300 ATK.

When an opponent's monster declares a direct attack.
[EFFECT]
Gain 800 LP. Then, draw 1 card and show it. Then, if that card is a Galaxy Type Normal Monster with 1600 or more ATK, negate the attack.

160013059.name: Recombination Galactica
160013059.description:

When your monster is destroyed by an opponent's attack.
[EFFECT]
Special Summon 1 Galaxy Type Normal Monster from your Graveyard face-up to your field.

[REQUIREMENT]

[EFFECT]
Draw 3 cards. Then, send 1 or more cards from your hand to the Graveyard. Then, if you have no monsters on your field, you take no battle damage from your opponent's Level 8 or lower monsters' attacks this turn.

160013061.name: Rose Chain Salvage
160013061.description:

When your opponent Special Summons a monster while you have a Level 6 or higher Spellcaster Type monster on your field equipped with an Equip Spell Card.
[EFFECT]
Special Summon 1 monster from your Graveyard face-up to your field. Then, gain LP equal to [the original Level of the monster Special Summoned by this effect] x 100.

160013062.description:

[EFFECT]

160013063.name: Nativity of the Monarchs
160013063.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
When your opponent Normal or Special Summons a Level 8 or lower monster face-up, send 1 monster from your field to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Special Summon 1 Level 5 or higher monster with 1000 DEF from your hand to your field in face-up Attack Position. Then, you can destroy 1 of those opponent's Normal or Special Summoned monsters.

160013064.name: Shared Sentiments
160013064.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
When your opponent Normal Summons a monster, shuffle 2 LIGHT Attribute monsters from your Graveyard into the Deck.
[EFFECT]
This turn, 1 face-up LIGHT Attribute monster on your field gains ATK equal to [the ATK of that Normal Summoned monster] and cannot be destroyed by your opponent's card effects.

160013065.name: Vortex of Shattered Light
160013065.description:

When your opponent Normal or Special Summons a Level 8 or lower monster face-up, shuffle 3 LIGHT Attribute Spellcaster Type monsters from your Graveyard into the Deck.
[EFFECT]
Destroy 1 of those Normal or Special Summoned monsters.

160013066.name: Rice Terrace Crisis

When your opponent Special Summons a monster from the hand or Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Change up to 2 face-up monsters on your opponent's field to face-down Defense Position, whose total Levels equal 12 or less.

160013122.name: Star Replacer

[REQUIREMENT]
If you have no other monsters on your field, return this card from your field to the owner's hand.
[EFFECT]
Special Summon 1 Level 4 or lower monster from your Graveyard to your field in face-down Defense Position. For the rest of this turn, you cannot Special Summon monsters from your hand or Graveyard.

160013130.name: Mad Rare Aquila

[REQUIREMENT]
If your opponent has 2 or more monsters on their field, send the top card of your Deck to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
This turn, this card can attack twice. Also, you can destroy 1 face-up Level 6 Effect Monster on your opponent's field. Then, if you destroyed a monster by this effect, this card gains 600 ATK until the end of this turn.

160013157.name: Protection of Arthenée

[REQUIREMENT]
Shuffle 1 monster from your Graveyard into the Deck, and equip this card to 1 face-up monster on your field.
[EFFECT]
The equipped monster cannot be destroyed by your opponent's card effects. Also, if you have an Equip Spell Card in your Graveyard, the equipped monster gains 300 ATK.

160013166.name: Rice Terrace Crisis
160013166.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
When your opponent Special Summons a monster from the hand or Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Change up to 2 face-up monsters on your opponent's field to face-down Defense Position, whose total Levels equal 12 or less.

160014000.name: Gaia The Fierce Knight (Rush)
160014000.description: A knight whose horse travels faster than the wind. His battle-charge is a force to be reckoned with.

160014001.name: Worm Drake (Rush)
160014001.description: Once this monster wraps itself around a victim, there is no escape.

160014002.name: Jointech Cobra
160014002.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
You have no other monsters on your field.
[EFFECT]
Special Summon 1 "Jointech Arcscorpio", "Jointech Spike Centipede", or "Jointech Rex" from your Graveyard to your field in face-up Defense Position. This turn, you cannot activate the effects of non-Machine Type monsters.

160014003.name: Mega Jointech Fortrex [L]
160014003.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Send 1 EARTH Attribute Machine Type monster from your hand to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
This card loses 600 ATK until the end of this turn. Then, toss a coin. If the result is heads, this card can attack 3 times this turn. If the result is tails, this turn, this card can make up to 2 attacks on monsters, and if it attacks a Defense Position monster, inflict piercing battle damage (if the ATK of the attacking monster exceeds the DEF of the attack target, inflict the difference).

160014004.name: Mega Jointech Fortrex
160014004.description:
MAXIMUM ATK = 3000
You can Maximum Summon this card together with "Mega Jointech Fortrex [L]" and "Mega Jointech Fortrex [R]".

[REQUIREMENT]
Maximum Mode
[CONTINUOUS EFFECT]
Increase this card's Level by 6. Also, if you have a Level 7 or higher Machine Type monster in your Graveyard, this card cannot be destroyed by card effects.

160014005.name: Mega Jointech Fortrex [R]

[REQUIREMENT]
None
[EFFECT]
Each player shuffles 3 monsters from their opponent's Graveyard into the owner's Deck. Then, if this card is in Maximum Mode, it gains ATK equal to [the total Levels of the EARTH Attribute Machine Type monsters shuffled by this effect] x 100 until the end of this turn.

Send 1 Machine Type monster from your hand or face-up from your field to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]

160014007.description:

Return 1 other face-up Level 5 or higher EARTH Attribute Machine Type monster from your field to the owner's hand.
[EFFECT]

160014008.description:

During the turn you Normal Summoned this card by Tributing "Jointech Ace", send the top card of your Deck to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
This card gains 1500 ATK until the end of this turn. Then, you can add 1 EARTH Attribute Machine Type monster from your Graveyard to your hand.

160014009.name: Chemipet Purr

[REQUIREMENT]
If you have a Pyro, Aqua, or Thunder Type monster in your Graveyard, send the top card of your Deck to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Gain 400 LP. Then, you can place 1 Pyro, Aqua, or Thunder Type monster from your Graveyard on top of your Deck.

160014010.name: Chemipet Woof

If you have 10 or less monsters in your Graveyard, send 2 cards from your hand to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Draw 1 card. Then, if you sent 2 Pyro, Aqua, and/or Thunder Type monsters to the Graveyard to meet the requirement, you can draw 1 additional card.

160014011.name: Melt the Aqueous Fairy
160014011.description:

[EFFECT]

160014012.name: Volt the Electrical Fairy
160014012.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Send 1 Level 4 or lower monster from your hand to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Add 1 Level 5 or 10 Pyro or Aqua Type monster from your Graveyard to your hand. Then, you can add 1 "Chemicalize Structure Force" from your Graveyard to your hand.

160014013.name: Hot the Combustible Fairy
160014013.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
During the turn you Normal Summoned this card.
[EFFECT]
Send cards from the top of your Deck to the Graveyard equal to [the number of different Types on your field]. Then, if you sent 2 or more Pyro Type monsters to the Graveyard by this effect, draw 1 card.

160014014.name: Ember the Hyper Assistant
160014014.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
If your opponent has a monster on their field, send this face-up card from your field to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Special Summon 1 Level 7 or higher Pyro Type monster from your hand face-up to your field. If you have "Ember the Super Assistant" in your Graveyard, then the monster Special Summoned by this effect gains 800 ATK until the end of this turn.

160014015.name: Blazebolt Chemistorm Fenghuang Volcalize Phoenix [L]
160014015.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Shuffle 1 FIRE Attribute Thunder Type monster from your Graveyard into the Deck.
[EFFECT]
Destroy 1 face-up Level 9 or lower monster on your opponent's field. Then, if this card is in Maximum Mode, you can destroy 1 monster on your opponent's field.

160014016.name: Blazebolt Chemistorm Fenghuang Volcalize Phoenix
160014016.description:
MAXIMUM ATK = 3500
You can Maximum Summon this card together with "Blazebolt Chemistorm Fenghuang Volcalize Phoenix [L]" and "Blazebolt Chemistorm Fenghuang Volcalize Phoenix [R]".

[REQUIREMENT]
Maximum Mode: Send 1 FIRE Attribute or Pyro Type monster from your hand to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Inflict 1000 damage to your opponent. Also, this turn, this card cannot be destroyed by your opponent's Trap Card effects, and if it attacks a Defense Position monster, inflict piercing battle damage (if the ATK of the attacking monster exceeds the DEF of the attack target, inflict the difference).

160014017.name: Blazebolt Chemistorm Fenghuang Volcalize Phoenix [R]
160014017.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Shuffle 1 FIRE Attribute Aqua Type monster from your Graveyard into the Deck.
[EFFECT]
Destroy 1 Spell/Trap Card on your opponent's field. Then, if this card is in Maximum Mode, you can destroy 1 Spell/Trap Card on your opponent's field.

160014018.name: Agent Miscast
160014018.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
If you have no other monsters on your field, pay 300 LP.
[EFFECT]
Send the top 3 cards of your Deck to the Graveyard. Then, if a Reptile Type monster(s) is among the cards sent, you can add 1 LIGHT Attribute Reptile Type monster from your Graveyard to your hand.

160014019.name: Agent Mistake
160014019.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
During your Main Phase this card was Normal or Special Summoned.
[EFFECT]
Excavate the top 3 cards of your Deck. You can add 1 excavated Level 3 or higher Reptile Type monster to your hand. Place the remaining cards on the top of the Deck in any order.

160014020.name: Agent Mismatch
160014020.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
If your opponent has a face-up Level 7 or higher monster on their field, send 1 Level 3 or lower Reptile Type monster from your hand to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Special Summon 1 Level 7 Reptile Type monster from your Graveyard to your field in face-up Attack Position.

160014021.name: Agent Mislead
160014021.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
If you have another face-up Reptile Type monster on your field, pay 300 LP.
[EFFECT]
Change 1 face-down Defense Position monster on either side of the field to face-up Attack Position. Then, this card loses 1300 ATK until the end of this turn.

160014022.name: Elite Agent Mystery
160014022.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Shuffle 2 other face-up Reptile Type monsters from your field and 1 card from your hand into the owner's Deck.
[EFFECT]
This card gains 300 ATK until the end of this turn. Then, you can Special Summon up to 2 Level 7 or higher Reptile Type monsters from your hand and/or Graveyard face-up to your field.

160014023.name: Abysslayer Leviaknight
160014023.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
None
[CONTINUOUS EFFECT]
This card gains ATK equal to [the number of Level 10 or higher Sea Serpent Type monsters in your Graveyard] x 500. Then, if you have 3 or more Level 10 or higher Sea Serpent Type monsters in your Graveyard, this card cannot be destroyed by your opponent's card effects during their turn.

160014024.name: Abysskite Ange
160014024.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Send 1 Sea Serpent Type monster from your hand to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Draw 1 card. Then, you can add 1 Level 10 Sea Serpent Type monster with 2500 ATK or "Abysskite Ultimail" from your Graveyard to your hand.

160014025.description:
[REQUIREMENT]

[EFFECT]

160014026.name: Abysskite Karen
160014026.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Send 1 LIGHT Attribute monster from your hand to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]

160014027.name: Constructor Driver Soldier Trailon

160014028.name: Change Slime - Dragon Champion Mode
160014028.description:

None

[EFFECT]
Look at 1 face-down card on your opponent's field. Then, if that card is a Monster Card with 1500 or more DEF, you can destroy it.

160014041.name: Landporter MAX

None

None

● Destroy 1 Spell/Trap Card on your opponent's field.

160014135.name: Specter of Heaven's Beginning

[EFFECT]

None

During the turn you have not Special Summoned a monster.

160015000.name: Esperade the Smashing Superstar
160015000.description:

Your LP are 1000 or lower.
[EFFECT]

160015001.name: Darkness Drake
160015001.description: The incarnation of darkness that deceives and corrupts one's mind. It eats away at everything.

160015002.name: Surging-Wave Swordsman Yoshimitsu Shark

[EFFECT]

Destroy 1 card on your opponent's field. Then, you can make this card gain ATK equal to [the original Level of the monster destroyed by this effect] x 200 until the end of this turn.

160015006.name: Flap Dragon

160015007.name: Flip Dragon

Change 1 Attack Position monster on your opponent's field to face-down Defense Position. Then, if the only face-up monsters on your field are Dragon Type monsters, you can Special Summon 1 "Flap Dragon" from your Graveyard to your field in face-up Defense Position.

Then, if 2 or more monsters are among the cards sent, this turn, this face-up card can be treated as 2 Tributes for the Tribute Summon of a Wyrm Type monster in Attack Position.
