160015013.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Your opponent has a face-up Level 7 or higher monster on their field.
[EFFECT]
Send the top 2 cards of your Deck to the Graveyard. If an Equip Spell Card(s) is among the cards sent, you can draw 1 card.

160015014.name: Plandolin
160015014.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Pay 100 LP.
[EFFECT]
Excavate the top 3 cards of your Deck. You can add up to 2 excavated "Fusion" and/or "Psyquip Fusion" to your hand. Shuffle the remaining cards into the Deck.

160015015.name: Star's Hand Camera Lady
160015015.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
During your Main Phase this card was Normal or Special Summoned.
[EFFECT]
Send the top 2 cards of your Deck to the Graveyard. Then, if you have "Esperade the Smashing Superstar" face-up on your field, you can destroy 1 Spell/Trap Card on your opponent's field.

160015016.name: Surging-Wave Swordsman Tanegashima Tuna
160015016.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
If you have a Level 7 Fish Type monster, "Fusion", or "Wave Fusion" in your Graveyard, send 1 card from your hand to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Add 1 Level 7 Fish Type monster, "Fusion", or "Wave Fusion" from your Graveyard to your hand.

160015017.name: Hydro Gun Mini Bluefin
160015017.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Send the top card of your Deck to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
This card gains ATK equal to [the total Levels of the face-up Fish Type monsters on your field] x 100 until the end of this turn. Then, you can take 1 "Hydro Cannon Big Bluefin" from your Graveyard, and either add it to your hand or Special Summon it face-up to your field.

160015018.name: Charge Remora
160015018.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Send 1 Fish Type monster from your hand to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Set 1 "Fish Depth Charge" from your Graveyard in your Spell & Trap Zone.

160015019.name: Carrier Manta Ray
160015019.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
During the turn you Normal Summoned this card.
[EFFECT]
Send the top 2 cards of your Deck to the Graveyard. Then, you can add 1 "Charge Remora" or 1 "Fish Depth Charge" from among the cards sent to the Graveyard by this effect to your hand.

160015020.name: Cyber Fish
160015020.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Send 1 WATER Attribute Fish Type monster from your hand to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Draw 1 card.

160015021.name: Cyber Shark (Rush)
160015021.description:
If you have a face-up WATER Attribute monster on your field, you can Normal Summon this card without Tributing.

[REQUIREMENT]
None
[EFFECT]
None

160015022.name: Surging-Wave Swordsman Onimaru Kunituna
160015022.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
None
[CONTINUOUS EFFECT]
Face-up Fish Type monsters on your field cannot be destroyed by your opponent's card effects.

160015023.name: Pandemonium Kappa River Sprinter
160015023.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Send 1 "Kappa Emperor River Slider", "Pandemonium Kappa Dive Wet", or "Kappa's Blast" from your hand to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Destroy 1 card on your opponent's field. Then, if you have 3 or more Aqua Type monsters in your Graveyard, you can draw 1 card.

160015024.name: Meteorite Dragon's Chick
160015024.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
During the turn you Normal Summoned this card.
[EFFECT]
Add 1 EARTH Attribute Dragon Type monster with 1800 ATK from your Graveyard to your hand.

160015025.name: Red-Eyes Moon Dragon
160015025.description:
This card's name becomes "Red-Eyes Black Dragon" while in the hand.

[REQUIREMENT]
None
[CONTINUOUS EFFECT]
If this card is used as material for a Fusion Summon, its name becomes "Red-Eyes Black Dragon".

160015026.name: Alligator's Black Knight
160015026.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
You have "Alligator's Sword" or a DARK Attribute monster with 1200 DEF in your Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Change 1 face-up Level 8 or lower monster on your opponent's field to face-down Defense Position.

160015027.name: Rocket Satellite Medic
160015027.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Place 1 card from your hand on the bottom of the Deck.
[EFFECT]
Add 1 "Meteor Dragon" or 1 "Meteor Flare Fusion" from your Graveyard to your hand.

160015028.name: Meteor Drake
160015028.description:
If you have no monsters on your field, you can Special Summon this card from your hand face-up to your field.

[REQUIREMENT]
None
[EFFECT]
Excavate the top 4 cards of your Deck. You can add 1 excavated "Meteor Dragon" or "Meteor Flare Fusion" to your hand. Place the remaining cards on the bottom of your Deck in any order.

160015029.name: Planting Pixie
160015029.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
2 or more face-up monsters with the same Attribute are on the field.
[EFFECT]
Add 1 Level 6 or lower Normal Monster or 1 "Fusion" from your Graveyard to your hand. Then, you can Special Summon 1 EARTH Attribute Plant Type monster from your hand face-up to your field.

160015030.name: Pure Love Angel
160015030.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
None
[CONTINUOUS EFFECT]
This card cannot be destroyed by battle with a monster with 2500 or more ATK. If this card battles a Level 9 or lower monster, you take no battle damage.

160015031.name: Owlchannel
160015031.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
If your opponent has 2 or more cards on their field, send the top card of your Deck to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
This turn, you take no damage from your opponent's Trap Card effects. Then, you can add 1 Winged Beast Type monster with 2200 ATK from your Graveyard to your hand.

160015032.name: Dark Effigy (Rush)
160015032.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
None
[CONTINUOUS EFFECT]
This face-up card can be treated as 2 Tributes for the Tribute Summon of a DARK Attribute Normal Monster in Attack Position.

160015033.name: Dead End the Mad Fiend of Despair
160015033.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Shuffle 4 monsters from your Graveyard into the Deck.
[EFFECT]
Destroy 1 face-up Level 8 or lower monster on your opponent's field. Then, if you have 6 or more monsters with the same Attribute in your Graveyard, you can Special Summon 1 Level 7 or lower monster from your opponent's Graveyard face-up to your field.

160015034.name: Glacies the Snowmeister of Sacred Splendor
160015034.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Send up to 6 other cards from your hand and/or field to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Until the end of your opponent's next turn, this card's Level is increased by 1, and it cannot be destroyed by your opponent's card effects. Then, you can shuffle up to 1 face-down card from your opponent's field into the owner's Deck for every 3 cards sent to the Graveyard to meet the requirement.

160015035.name: Darkness Doom Giant
160015035.description:
"Darkness Dwarf" + 1 LIGHT Attribute or DARK Attribute Galaxy Type monster

[REQUIREMENT]
None
[EFFECT]
Add 1 Level 7 or 8 Galaxy Type monster or 1 "Fusion" from your Graveyard to your hand. Then, this turn, this face-up card can be treated as 2 or 3 Tributes for the Tribute Summon of a Level 8 Galaxy Type monster in Attack Position.

160015036.name: Darkness Galactica Oblivion
160015036.description:
"Galactica Oblivion" + "Darkness Dwarf"

[REQUIREMENT]
Send the top card of your Deck to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
1 face-up Effect Monster with 100 or more original ATK on your opponent's field loses ATK equal to [its original ATK] until the end of this turn. Then, you can negate its Continuous Effects until the end of this turn.

160015037.name: Red Reboot Enhanced Boost Dragon
160015037.description:
"Red Boot Boost Dragon" + "Darkness Drake"

[REQUIREMENT]
Shuffle 1 monster from your Graveyard into the Deck.
[EFFECT]
Choose up to 3 DARK Attribute monsters in your Graveyard. Inflict damage to your opponent equal to [the total Levels of the chosen monsters] x 100, and this card gains ATK equal to [the total Levels of the chosen monsters] x 100 until the end of this turn. Then, shuffle the chosen monsters into the Deck.

160015038.name: Celeb Rose Gossip Witch
160015038.description:
"Celeb Rose Witch" + "Darkness Paparazzi"

[REQUIREMENT]
None
[EFFECT]
Destroy 1 Spell/Trap Card on your opponent's field. Then, if you have a face-up Spell Card on your field, draw 1 card.

160015039.name: Celeb Rose Gossip Magician
160015039.description:
"Celeb Rose Magician" + "Darkness Paparazzi"

[REQUIREMENT]
None
[CONTINUOUS EFFECT]
This card gains ATK equal to [the number of Equip Spell Cards in your Graveyard] x 400. If you have a face-up Spell Card on your field, this card cannot be destroyed by battle.

160015040.name: Demolition Meltdown Dragon Darkness Blasthamut
160015040.description:
"Demolition Dragon Blasthamut" + "Darkness Phantomite"

[REQUIREMENT]
None
[EFFECT]
Send the top 3 cards of your opponent's Deck to the Graveyard. Then, if a monster(s) is among the cards sent, you can destroy face-down cards on your opponent's field, up to [the number of monsters sent to the Graveyard by this effect]. Then, inflict damage to your opponent equal to [the number of cards destroyed by this effect] x 500.

160015041.name: Bluegrass High Stealer
160015041.description:
"Bluegrass Stealer" + "Fiddlebadour"

[REQUIREMENT]
If you have a face-up Spell Card on your field, send the top card of your Deck to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Return 1 Spell/Trap Card from the field to the owner's hand. Then, you can add 1 "Fiddlebadour" from your Graveyard to your hand.

160015042.name: Bandiva the Ballistic Battle Ballad
160015042.description:
"Bandijo the Battle Ballad" + "Fiddlebadour"

[REQUIREMENT]
None
[EFFECT]
Draw 1 card. Then, this card gains ATK equal to [the total number of cards in both players' hands] x 500 until the end of your opponent's next turn. Then, if you have exactly 1 card in your hand, you can destroy 1 card on your opponent's field.

160015043.name: Plectclive the Dynamauve Deadly Dirge
160015043.description:
"Plectcrime of the Deadly Dirge" + "Fiddlebadour"

[REQUIREMENT]
Reveal up to 2 Spell Cards in your hand to your opponent.
[EFFECT]
Special Summon Level 8 or lower WIND Attribute Psychic Type monsters from your Graveyard equal to [the number of cards revealed to meet the requirement] face-up to your field.

160015044.name: Dark Hydro Cannon Neutron Bluefin
160015044.description:
"Hydro Cannon Big Bluefin" + "Surging-Wave Swordsman Tanegashima Tuna"

[REQUIREMENT]
None
[CONTINUOUS EFFECT]
If the only face-up monsters on your field are Fusion Monsters, this card can attack directly. If your opponent has a face-up Maximum Monster on their field, your opponent cannot activate monster effects.

160015045.name: Pitch-Dark Surging-Wave Swordsman Onimaru Kunituna
160015045.description:
"Surging-Wave Swordsman Onimaru Kunituna" + "Hydro Gun Mini Bluefin"

[REQUIREMENT]
None
[CONTINUOUS EFFECT]
If this card attacks a Defense Position monster, inflict piercing battle damage (if the ATK of the attacking monster exceeds the DEF of the attack target, inflict the difference). Face-up Fish Type monsters on your field cannot be destroyed by your opponent's card effects.

160015046.name: Meteor Swarm Dragon
160015046.description:
"Meteor Dragon" + "Meteor Drake"

[REQUIREMENT]
None
[EFFECT]
Special Summon 1 EARTH Attribute Dragon Type monster with 1800 ATK from your Graveyard to your field in face-up Defense Position.

160015047.name: Meteor Black Drake
160015047.description:
"Red-Eyes Black Dragon" + "Meteor Drake"

[REQUIREMENT]
If you have "Meteor Flare Fusion" in your Graveyard, send the top card of your Deck to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
This card cannot be destroyed by your opponent's card effects until the end of your opponent's next turn. Then, if you have 2 or more "Meteor Flare Fusion" in your Graveyard, inflict 500 damage to your opponent.

160015048.name: Meteor Black Mars Dragon
160015048.description:
"Red-Eyes Black Dragon" + "Meteor Dragon"

[REQUIREMENT]
If you have "Meteor Dragon" in your Graveyard, send the top card of your Deck to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Until the end of this turn, this card gains ATK equal to [the number of monsters in your Graveyard] x 200, and if it attacks a Defense Position monster, inflict piercing battle damage (if the ATK of the attacking monster exceeds the DEF of the attack target, inflict the difference).

160015049.name: Galflare the Skysavior Shine
160015049.description:
"Ranga the Skysavior Knight" + "Soleil the Skysavior Angel"

[REQUIREMENT]
Place 1 card from your hand on the bottom of the Deck.
[MULTI-CHOICE EFFECT]
● Shuffle cards from your opponent's Graveyard into the Deck, up to [the number of face-up Celestial Warrior Type monsters on your field] x 2.
● Add 1 Level 4 or lower LIGHT or DARK Attribute monster or 1 "Skysavior Wish" from your Graveyard to your hand.

160015050.name: Dragonic Progression
160015050.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Place 1 card from your hand on the bottom of the Deck.
[EFFECT]
Add 1 Level 1 LIGHT or DARK Attribute Dragon Type monster from your Graveyard to your hand. Then, you can add 1 "Dragons Burst Fusion" or 1 "Dragons Boost Fusion" from your Graveyard to your hand.

160015051.name: Psyquip Fusion
160015051.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
None
[EFFECT]
Fusion Summon by sending face-up Psychic Type monsters from your field to the Graveyard as material. Then, if you have a WIND Attribute monster in your Graveyard, you can add 1 Equip Spell Card from your Graveyard to your hand.

160015052.name: Miracle Pick
160015052.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Reveal 1 Level 7 LIGHT Attribute or DARK Attribute Psychic Type monster with 0 DEF in your hand to your opponent.
[EFFECT]
Excavate the top 3 cards of your Deck. Add 1 excavated card to your hand. Send the remaining cards to the Graveyard. You can only attack with Omega Psychic Type or Psychic Type monsters this turn.

160015053.name: Autumn Leaves of Blisstopia
160015053.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Activate this card by placing 1 Wyrm Type monster from your Graveyard on top of your Deck.
[EFFECT]
While this card is face-up in the Field Zone, face-up Wyrm Type monsters on the field gain 300 ATK, and if they attack a Defense Position monster, inflict piercing battle damage (if the ATK of the attacking monster exceeds the DEF of the attack target, inflict the difference).

160015054.name: Wave Fusion
160015054.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
You have 5 or more WATER Attribute Fish Type monsters in your Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Fusion Summon a WATER Attribute Fish Type monster by shuffling WATER Attribute Fish Type monsters from your field and/or Graveyard into the Deck as material.

160015055.name: Raging Waves
160015055.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
None
[EFFECT]
While this card is face-up in the Field Zone, a player that has exactly 1 monster on their field can only attack monsters with Fish/Sea Serpent/Thunder/Aqua Type monsters.

160015056.name: Salvage (Rush)
160015056.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
None
[EFFECT]
Add 2 WATER Attribute monsters with 1500 or less ATK from your Graveyard to your hand.

160015057.name: Meteor Flare Fusion
160015057.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
None
[EFFECT]
Fusion Summon by sending 2 monsters from your hand and/or field to the Graveyard as material, including "Red-Eyes Black Dragon", "Summoned Skull", or "Meteor Dragon". Then, if you Special Summoned a non-Effect Monster by this effect, you can destroy 1 card on your opponent's field.

160015058.name: Meteorite Dragon Nails
160015058.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Equip this card to 1 face-up EARTH, FIRE, or DARK Attribute Dragon Type monster on your field.
[EFFECT]
The equipped monster gains 300 ATK. Also, if the equipped monster is a non-Effect Fusion Monster, it gains 700 additional ATK and cannot be destroyed by your opponent's card effects.

160015059.name: Companions!
160015059.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
You have 2 face-up monsters with the same Type on your field.
[EFFECT]
Draw 1 card. Then, you can make 2 face-up monsters with the same Attribute on your field gain 400 ATK until the end of this turn.

160015060.name: Maid's Mischief
160015060.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Send the top 2 cards of your Deck to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Shuffle up to 2 monsters from your opponent's Graveyard into the Deck. Then, you can draw cards equal to [the number of Level 7 Effect Monsters shuffled by this effect].

160015061.name: Peace & Rock n' Roll
160015061.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
When your opponent Normal or Special Summons a monster while you have "Prima Guitarna the Shining Superstar" or "Esperade the Smashing Superstar" face-up on your field.
[EFFECT]
Destroy 1 monster on your opponent's field. Then, if your LP are 2000 or lower, this turn, you take no battle damage, also you take no damage from your opponent's card effects.

160015062.name: Fish Depth Charge (Rush)
160015062.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
When your opponent Normal or Special Summons a monster, or after your opponent activates a Spell Card, send 1 face-up Fish Type monster from your field to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Destroy 1 card on your opponent's field. Then, draw 1 card.

160015063.name: Meteorite Fall
160015063.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
When an opponent's monster declares an attack while you have 3 or more Dragon Type monsters in your Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
The attacking monster loses 1000 ATK until the end of this turn. Then, you can Set 1 "Meteor Flare Fusion" from your Graveyard in your Spell & Trap Zone.

160015064.name: Skysavior Wish
160015064.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
When your opponent Normal or Special Summons a monster, place 1 WATER Attribute Warrior Type monster and 1 Fairy Type monster from your Graveyard on top of your Deck in any order.
[EFFECT]
Place 1 monster from your opponent's field on the bottom of the owner's Deck. Then, you can Set 1 "Skysavior Watch" or 1 "Fusion" from your Graveyard in your Spell & Trap Zone.

160015065.name: Star Salvation Shield
160015065.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
When your opponent draws a card during their turn, or when your opponent Normal or Special Summons a monster during their turn, send 1 monster from your field to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Your opponent can only declare an attack once this turn. Then, you can take control of 1 face-up Level 9 or higher Magical Knight Type Fusion Monster whose original ATK is 3000 on your opponent's field.

160015066.name: Fusion Cancel
160015066.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
When a monster(s) is destroyed by battle.
[EFFECT]
Return 1 face-up Fusion Monster from the field to the owner's Extra Deck. Then, if all of the materials' names are specifically listed on the returned monster, its owner can Special Summon all of them from their Graveyard face-up to their field.

160015121.name: Cyber Shark (Rush)
160015121.description:
If you have a face-up WATER Attribute monster on your field, you can Normal Summon this card without Tributing.

[REQUIREMENT]
None
[EFFECT]
None

160015130.name: Pure Love Angel
160015130.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
None
[CONTINUOUS EFFECT]
This card cannot be destroyed by battle with a monster with 2500 or more ATK. If this card battles a Level 9 or lower monster, you take no battle damage.

160015160.name: Maid's Mischief
160015160.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Send the top 2 cards of your Deck to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Shuffle up to 2 monsters from your opponent's Graveyard into the Deck. Then, you can draw cards equal to [the number of Level 7 Effect Monsters shuffled by this effect].

160015166.name: Fusion Cancel
160015166.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
When a monster(s) is destroyed by battle.
[EFFECT]
Return 1 face-up Fusion Monster from the field to the owner's Extra Deck. Then, if all of the materials' names are specifically listed on the returned monster, its owner can Special Summon all of them from their Graveyard face-up to their field.

160016001.name: Praime Dwarf
160016001.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
None
[EFFECT]
Send 1 monster from your field to the Graveyard. Then, you can shuffle 3 LIGHT Attribute monsters with different Types from your Graveyard into the Deck. If you do, you can Fusion Summon 1 LIGHT Attribute monster by sending LIGHT Attribute monsters from among the face-up monsters on the field to the Graveyard as material.

160016002.name: Praime Phantomite
160016002.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Shuffle 2 LIGHT Attribute monsters from your Graveyard into the Deck.
[EFFECT]
Change 1 Level 7 or higher Attack Position monster on the field to face-down Defense Position. Then, each player excavates the top 3 cards of their Deck. Each player places their excavated cards on top of their Deck in any order.

160016003.name: Interspraime
160016003.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
If the only monsters in your Graveyard are LIGHT Attribute monsters, reveal 1 Level 7 or 8 Effect Monster in your hand.
[EFFECT]
Send the top 3 cards of your Deck to the Graveyard. Then, you can add 1 "Transam Praime Armor Nova" or "Transam Linac" from your Graveyard to your hand.

160016004.name: Praime Claw Girl
160016004.description:
You can Tribute Summon this card in Attack Position by Tributing 1 monster. If you do, its original ATK becomes 200.

[REQUIREMENT]
Place 2 cards from your hand on the bottom of the Deck in any order.
[EFFECT]
Special Summon 1 LIGHT Attribute Normal Monster from your Graveyard to your field in face-up Defense Position. Then, you can add 1 "Fusion" from your Graveyard to your hand.

160016005.name: Praime Tractiger
160016005.description:
You can Tribute Summon this card in Attack Position by Tributing 1 monster. If you do, its original ATK becomes 1800.

[REQUIREMENT]
Send 1 monster from your hand to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Choose 1 face-up monster on your field. If it attacks a Defense Position monster this turn, inflict piercing battle damage (if the ATK of the attacking monster exceeds the DEF of the attack target, inflict the difference).

160016006.name: Praime Bandijo
160016006.description:
You can Tribute Summon this card in Attack Position by Tributing 1 monster. If you do, its original ATK becomes 1800.

[REQUIREMENT]
Pay 1000 LP.
[EFFECT]
Add 1 Level 4 or lower LIGHT Attribute Normal Monster or 1 "Praime Call" from your Graveyard to your hand, and this card gains 500 ATK until the end of this turn.

160016007.name: Praime Dian Keto
160016007.description:
You can Tribute Summon this card in Attack Position by Tributing 1 monster. If you do, its original ATK becomes 1000.

[REQUIREMENT]
Send 1 monster from your hand to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Gain 1000 LP, and this card gains 1000 ATK until the end of this turn. Then, you can add 1 "Praime Call" from your Graveyard to your hand.

160016008.name: Transam Praime Armor Nova
160016008.description:
You can Tribute Summon this card in Attack Position by Tributing 1 or 3 monsters. If you Tributed 1 this way, its original ATK becomes 1800.

[REQUIREMENT]
None
[CONTINUOUS EFFECT]
This card that was Normal Summoned by Tributing 3 monsters gains ATK equal to [the total original Levels of the monsters Tributed for its Normal Summon] x 100.

160016009.name: Dice Angel
160016009.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Send 1 card from your hand to the Graveyard, except "Graceful Dice".
[EFFECT]
Add 1 "Graceful Dice" from your Graveyard to your hand. Then, if your opponent has 2 or more monsters on their field, roll a six-sided die. If you roll a number other than 6, gain 600 LP.

160016010.name: Dice Demon
160016010.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Send 1 card from your hand to the Graveyard, except "Skull Dice".
[EFFECT]
Add 1 "Skull Dice" from your Graveyard to your hand. Then, if your opponent has 2 or more monsters on their field, roll a six-sided die. If you roll a number other than 1, inflict 600 damage to your opponent.

160016011.name: Dice Archswordsman
160016011.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
None
[EFFECT]
Roll a six-sided die. This card can attack a number of times equal to [the result] during this turn. Then, if the result was 3 or lower, you can draw 1 card.

160016012.name: Dice Archangel
160016012.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
None
[EFFECT]
Roll a six-sided die. Until the end of this turn, all face-up monsters on your field gain ATK/DEF equal to [the result] x 100, or [the result] x 200 instead if you have "Graceful Dice" in your Graveyard.

160016013.name: Dice Archdemon
160016013.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
None
[EFFECT]
Roll a six-sided die. Until the end of this turn, all face-up monsters on your opponent's field lose ATK/DEF equal to [the result] x 100, or [the result] x 200 instead if you have "Skull Dice" in your Graveyard.

160016014.name: Dice Key Caramail
160016014.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
None
[CONTINUOUS EFFECT]
While you have a face-up Level 7 or higher monster with an effect that requires a die roll on your field, your opponent cannot activate Trap Cards during the Battle Phase.

160016015.name: Dice Key Minna
160016015.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
If you have a face-up monster with an effect that requires a die roll on your field, send the top card of your Deck to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
All face-up monsters on your field gain 600 ATK until the end of your opponent's next turn. Then, you can add 1 Fairy Type monster with 300 ATK/1200 DEF from your Graveyard to your hand.

160016016.name: Dicemite Girl Chirori
160016016.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
None
[EFFECT]
Roll a six-sided die and apply the result until the end of this turn.
● 1 or 2: This card loses 1000 ATK.
● 3 or 4: This card gains 600 ATK.
● 5 or 6: This card gains ATK equal to [the original ATK of 1 face-up monster on your opponent's field].

160016017.name: Jointech Nesstrydar Tank
160016017.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Shuffle 2 cards from your hand into the Deck.
[EFFECT]
Special Summon 1 Level 7 or 8 DARK Attribute monster from your Graveyard face-up to your field. If you do, until the end of this turn, you can only Special Summon "Jointech Tridynabase", and you cannot activate the effects of DARK Attribute monsters.

160016018.name: Darkness Jointech Tyrant
160016018.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
During a turn you have not activated a monster effect.
[EFFECT]
Add 2 Level 7 or 8 DARK Attribute monsters with different Types from your Graveyard to your hand. Then, this card's name becomes "Jointech Nesstrydar Tank" this turn.

160016019.name: Vande the Electric Lion
160016019.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
You have 2 or less monsters on your field.
[EFFECT]
Send cards from the top of your Deck to the Graveyard equal to [the number of face-up Pyro, Aqua, and/or Thunder Type monsters on your field] x 2.

160016020.name: James the Steam Swallow
160016020.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Your opponent has a monster on their field.
[EFFECT]
Special Summon 1 Level 2 or lower FIRE Attribute Thunder Type monster from your Graveyard to your field in face-up Defense Position. Then, you can Set 1 "Fusion" from your Graveyard in your Spell & Trap Zone.

160016021.name: Abysslayer Quintiamat
160016021.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Shuffle up to 3 monsters from your Graveyard into the Deck, including a Sea Serpent Type Maximum Monster.
[EFFECT]
Draw 1 card. Then, you can excavate the top 5 cards of your Deck. You can add up to 3 excavated Level 7 or higher Sea Serpent Type monsters to your hand. Place the remaining cards on the bottom of your Deck in any order.

160016022.name: Agent Mishap
160016022.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
During the turn you Normal Summoned this card, pay 300 LP.
[EFFECT]
Inflict damage to your opponent equal to [the number of face-up LIGHT Attribute Reptile Type monsters on your field] x 300. You can only attack with Reptile Type monsters this turn.

160016023.name: Secret Base Guardian Misshot
160016023.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Shuffle 3 Level 3 LIGHT Attribute Reptile Type monsters from your Graveyard into the Deck.
[EFFECT]
This card gains 3000 ATK until the end of your opponent's next turn. Then, if you activated this effect during the turn you Normal Summoned this card by Tributing "Elite Agent Mystery", you can destroy up to 3 face-up Level 8 or lower monsters on your opponent's field.

160016024.name: Sevens Fear Magician
160016024.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Send the top card of your Deck to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
This card's name becomes "Sevens Road Magician" this turn. Then, you can make 1 face-up monster on your opponent's field lose ATK equal to [the number of different Attributes in your Graveyard] x 300 until the end of this turn.

160016025.name: CAN - St:D
160016025.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
If the only monsters in your Graveyard are Omega Psychic Type and/or Psychic Type, send 1 card from the hand to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Return 1 face-up monster from your opponent's field to the owner's hand. Then, if you have "CAN:D" in your Graveyard, gain 700 LP.

160016026.name: Jinzo #7.7
160016026.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Place 1 monster from your Graveyard on the bottom of the Deck.
[EFFECT]
This card can attack directly this turn. Then, you can add 1 "Machine Inspector" or 1 "Accelerator" from your Graveyard to your hand.

160016027.name: Jinzo - Returner (Rush)
160016027.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Send this face-up card from your field to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Special Summon 1 "Jinzo" from your Graveyard face-up to your field.

160016028.name: Jinzo the Machine Menace (Rush)
160016028.description:
If a player has a Trap Card in their Graveyard, you can Special Summon this card from your hand face-up to your field.

[REQUIREMENT]
Send this face-up card from your field to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Special Summon 1 "Jinzo" from your Graveyard face-up to your field. Then, you can look at all face-down cards in your opponent's Spell & Trap Zone, then return them to their original positions. If you do, destroy all Trap Cards among them.

160016029.name: Jinzo - Amplified
160016029.description:
This card's name becomes "Jinzo" while in the Graveyard.

[REQUIREMENT]
Send the top card of your Deck to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
This card cannot be destroyed by your opponent's Trap Card effects this turn. Then, you can make this card gain ATK equal to [the number of Machine Type monsters in your Graveyard] x 100 until the end of this turn.

160016030.name: Catapult Baby Turtle
160016030.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Send 1 card from your hand to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Shuffle 2 monsters from your opponent's Graveyard into the Deck. Then, you can Special Summon 1 "Gaia the Dragon Champion" or 1 Aqua Type monster with 2000 DEF from your Graveyard face-up to your field.

160016031.name: Animagica Witch
160016031.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Reveal up to 2 Level 7 or 8 LIGHT Attribute Effect Monsters in your hand to your opponent.
[EFFECT]
Draw cards equal to [the number of monsters revealed to meet the requirement]. Then, shuffle cards from your hand into the Deck equal to [the number of cards drawn by this effect].

160016032.name: Obnoxious Celtic Guard (Rush)
160016032.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
None
[CONTINUOUS EFFECT]
This card cannot be destroyed by battle with a monster that has 1900 or more ATK.

160016033.name: Snipe Hunter (Rush)
160016033.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Send any number of cards from your hand to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Roll a six-sided die a number of times equal to [the number of cards sent to the Graveyard to meet the requirement]. Destroy cards on your opponent's field, up to [the number of times you rolled a number other than 1 or 6].

160016034.name: Golden Flying Fish (Rush)
160016034.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Send 1 other face-up Fish Type monster from your field to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Destroy 1 card on the field.

160016035.name: Mist Assassin
160016035.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Send 1 monster from your field to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Add up to 2 "Fusion" and/or "Fusion Cancel" from your Graveyard to your hand.

160016036.name: Deity of Seven Treasures - Ryozai
160016036.description:
If you have a monster with 2700 DEF or "Ship of Seven Treasures" in your Graveyard, you can Special Summon this card from your hand face-up to your field.

[REQUIREMENT]
None
[CONTINUOUS EFFECT]
Face-up Level 7 monsters on your field and face-down Spell/Trap Cards on your field cannot be destroyed by your opponent's card effects.

160016037.name: Praime Pierce Giant
160016037.description:
"Praime Dwarf" + 1 Level 8 or lower LIGHT Attribute monster

[REQUIREMENT]
None
[CONTINUOUS EFFECT]
If your Level 7 or higher LIGHT Attribute monster attacks a Defense Position monster, inflict piercing battle damage (if the ATK of the attacking monster exceeds the DEF of the attack target, inflict the difference). During your opponent's turn, monsters on your field cannot be used as material for a Fusion Summon.

160016038.name: Praime Cat Straynya
160016038.description:
"Praime Claw Girl" + 1 LIGHT Attribute monster

[REQUIREMENT]
None
[CONTINUOUS EFFECT]
Face-up Level 7 or higher LIGHT Attribute monsters on your field gain 200 ATK and cannot be destroyed by your opponent's card effects.

160016039.name: Transam Praime Full Armor Nova
160016039.description:
"Transam Praime Armor Nova" + "Transam Linac"
[REQUIREMENT]
None
[CONTINUOUS EFFECT]
This card gains ATK equal to [the number of different Types in both players' Graveyards] x 300. If there are 5 or more different Types in the Graveyards, this card cannot be destroyed by your opponent's card effects, then if there are 10 or more different Types in the Graveyards, this card gains an additional 3000 ATK.

160016040.name: Transamvelg Linac
160016040.description:
"Transam Linac" + "Voidvelg Requiem"
[REQUIREMENT]
Send the top 3 cards of your Deck to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
This card gains 900 ATK until the end of your opponent's next turn. Then, if you sent a LIGHT or DARK Attribute monster to the Graveyard to meet the requirement, you can make all face-up monsters on your opponent's field lose 1000 ATK until the end of their next turn.

160016041.name: Jointech Tridynabase
160016041.description:
"Jointech Nesstrydar Tank" + 2 non-Machine Type monsters

[REQUIREMENT]
None
[CONTINUOUS EFFECT]
If this card attacks a Defense Position monster, inflict piercing battle damage (if the ATK of the attacking monster exceeds the DEF of the attack target, inflict the difference). This card can make up to 3 attacks during the turn it was Fusion Summoned by sending monsters whose original names are "Voidvelg Requiem" and "Abysslayer Leviaknight" to the Graveyard as material.

160016042.name: Super Graphagas Archer
160016042.description:
"Chromatographagas" + "Ember the Super Assistant"
[REQUIREMENT]
Place 1 Level 7 Pyro Type Normal Monster from your Graveyard on top of the Deck.
[EFFECT]
This card gains 2500 ATK until the end of this turn. Then, you can make 1 face-up Level 9 or lower monster on your opponent's field lose 1500 ATK until the end of this turn.

160016043.name: Prophecy Flail of the Colors of the Wind, Butterflies and Flowers
160016043.description:
"Prophecy Phrase the Colors of the Wind" + "Fiddlebadour"

[REQUIREMENT]
None
[EFFECT]
Destroy 1 face-up Level 8 or lower monster on your opponent's field. Then, you can shuffle all monsters from your opponent's Graveyard into the Deck. If you do, this card gains 1200 ATK until the end of this turn, and you draw 1 card.

160016044.name: Celeb Rose Influencers
160016044.description:
"Celeb Rose Enchanter" + "Celeb Rose Wiz"

[REQUIREMENT]
None
[EFFECT]
Place 1 monster from your opponent's Graveyard on the bottom of the Deck, and this card gains ATK equal to [the Level of the monster placed by this effect] x 200 until the end of this turn. Then, if this card is equipped with an Equip Spell Card, this turn, this card cannot be destroyed by card effects and can make up to 2 attacks on monsters.

160016045.name: Murin Duke the Shadow Flower Wave
160016045.description:
"Flower Fan Clematis" + "Lindo the Shadow Flower Warrior"

[REQUIREMENT]
None
[EFFECT]
1 face-up monster on your field gains ATK equal to [the number of monsters on your field] x 500 until the end of this turn. Then, inflict 700 damage to your opponent.

160016046.name: Nelkrita the Skysavior Hadal
160016046.description:
"Seir the Skysavior Knight" + "Lua the Skysavior Angel"

[REQUIREMENT]
None
[CONTINUOUS EFFECT]
If your Celestial Warrior, Warrior, or Fairy Type monster equipped with an Equip Spell Card attacks a Defense Position monster, inflict piercing battle damage (if the ATK of the attacking monster exceeds the DEF of the attack target, inflict the difference).

160016047.name: Swift Gaia the Dragon Champion
160016047.description:
1 Warrior Type monster with 2100 DEF + "Curse of Dragon"

[REQUIREMENT]
Send the top card of your Deck to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
If this card attacks a Defense Position monster this turn, inflict piercing battle damage (if the ATK of the attacking monster exceeds the DEF of the attack target, inflict the difference). Then, if you have no cards in your hand, you can draw 1 card.

160016048.name: Praime Call
160016048.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
The only monsters in your Graveyard are LIGHT Attribute.
[EFFECT]
Add 1 monster from your Graveyard to your hand. Then, you can add 1 "Fusion" from your Graveyard to your hand. You cannot activate monster effects for the rest of this turn, except "Praime Dwarf".

160016049.name: Graceful Dice (Rush)
160016049.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
None
[EFFECT]
Roll a six-sided die. All face-up monsters on your field gain ATK/DEF equal to [the result] x 100 until the end of this turn.

160016050.name: Dice of Greed
160016050.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
If you have 10 or more cards in your Deck, send 3 cards with an effect that requires a die roll from your hand to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Roll a six-sided die. Draw cards equal to [the result]. Then, if the result is 3 or lower, you can add up to 2 "Graceful Dice" and/or "Skull Dice" from your Graveyard to your hand.

160016051.name: The Secret of Manifestation
160016051.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Send up to 2 monsters from your hand and/or field to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Draw 1 card. Then, you can Special Summon 1 Level 5 or higher LIGHT Attribute Spellcaster Type monster from your Graveyard face-up to your field. You cannot activate monster effects for the rest of this turn, except LIGHT Attribute Spellcaster Type monsters'.

160016052.name: Abysskite Mapping
160016052.description:
This card's name becomes "Abysskite Prevent Wall" while in the Graveyard.

[REQUIREMENT]
None
[EFFECT]
Gain LP equal to [the number of face-up Sea Serpent Type monsters on your field] x 300. Then, you can add 1 "Abysskite Party" from your Graveyard to your hand.

160016053.name: Secret Alteration
160016053.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Send 3 cards from your hand to the Graveyard, including 2 LIGHT Attribute Reptile Type monsters.
[EFFECT]
Draw 3 cards. Then, you can make 1 face-up Level 8 or lower monster on your opponent's field lose 1300 ATK until the end of this turn.

160016054.name: Secret Investigation Mobile Thunderbird
160016054.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Equip this card to 1 face-up LIGHT Attribute Reptile Type monster on your field.
[EFFECT]
The equipped monster gains 300 ATK, and can attack directly.

160016055.name: Royal Rebel's King's Return
160016055.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Send the top 2 cards of your Deck to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Reduce the Level of 1 face-up Level 3 or higher monster on your opponent's field by 2 until the end of this turn. Then, you can add 1 Level 7 or higher Fiend Type monster with 0 DEF from your Graveyard to your hand.

160016056.name: Accelerator
160016056.description:
This card's effect cannot be negated.

[REQUIREMENT]
Equip this card to 1 face-up Machine Type monster on your field.
[EFFECT]
The equipped monster gains 300 ATK. If the equipped monster's original name is "Jinzo", its Continuous Effect becomes "Your opponent cannot activate Trap Cards, and their Trap Card effects are negated".

160016057.name: Machine Inspector
160016057.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
None
[EFFECT]
Each player excavates the top 4 cards of their Deck. You can send up to 2 excavated Machine Type monsters and/or Trap Cards to the Graveyard. Each player places their remaining cards on the bottom of their Deck in any order. Then, if you sent a Trap Card to the Graveyard by this effect, draw 1 card.

160016058.name: Jointech Joint
160016058.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Shuffle 2 monsters from your Graveyard into the Deck.
[EFFECT]
Change 1 monster on your opponent's field to face-up Attack Position or face-down Defense Position. Then, you can Fusion Summon 1 Level 9 or lower EARTH Attribute or DARK Attribute Machine Type monster by sending monsters from your hand and/or field to the Graveyard as material.

160016059.name: Threat from Outer Space
160016059.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Pay 1000 LP.
[EFFECT]
Send the top card of your Deck to the Graveyard. Then, you can Set that card to your field (if it is a monster, you can Special Summon it in face-down Defense Position). Then, if you Special Summoned a Level 2 monster from the Graveyard by this effect, you can destroy 1 Spell/Trap Card on your opponent's field.

160016060.name: De-Spell (Rush)
160016060.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
None
[EFFECT]
Choose 1 face-up Spell Card or 1 face-down Spell/Trap Card on your opponent's field. If the chosen card is face-up, destroy it. If the chosen card is face-down, look at it, then return it to its original position. Then, if it was a Spell Card, destroy it.

160016061.name: Abysskite Ray Monochrome
160016061.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
When an opponent's monster declares an attack.
[EFFECT]
Shuffle 3 Level 4 or lower LIGHT Attribute and/or DARK Attribute monsters from the Graveyards into the owner's Decks. Then, the attacking monster loses ATK equal to [the total Levels of the monsters shuffled by this effect] x 200 until the end of this turn.

160016062.name: Skull Dice (Rush)
160016062.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
When an opponent's monster declares an attack.
[EFFECT]
Roll a six-sided die. All face-up monsters on your opponent's field lose ATK/DEF equal to [the result] x 100 until the end of this turn.

160016063.name: Asura Dice
160016063.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
When your opponent Normal or Special Summons a monster face-up.
[EFFECT]
Roll a six-sided die. Inflict damage to your opponent equal to [the result] x 100, and all face-up monsters on your opponent's field lose ATK/DEF equal to [the result] x 100 until the end of this turn. Then, you can make all face-up monsters on your field gain ATK/DEF equal to [the result] x 100 until the end of this turn.

160016064.name: Fusionic Defense
160016064.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
When your opponent Normal or Special Summons a monster.
[EFFECT]
Set 1 "Fusion" or 1 "Fusion Cancel" from your Graveyard in your Spell & Trap Zone. Then, you can choose 1 face-up monster on your field. If you do, it cannot be destroyed by battle or card effects this turn.

160016065.name: Secret File 3000 - Final Tragedy
160016065.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
When an opponent's monster declares an attack while you have 3 face-up LIGHT Attribute Reptile Type monsters on your field, shuffle 3 LIGHT Attribute Reptile Type monsters from your Graveyard into the Deck.
[EFFECT]
Destroy all Attack Position monsters on your opponent's field. Then, inflict 3000 damage to your opponent.

160016066.name: Sunset Rebirth
160016066.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
When your opponent draws a card during their turn, or when a monster on your field is destroyed by an opponent's card effect.
[EFFECT]
Special Summon 1 monster from your hand or Graveyard to your field in face-down Defense Position. Then, up to 3 other cards on your field cannot be destroyed by your opponent's card effects this turn.

160016116.name: Dicemite Girl Chirori
160016116.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
None
[EFFECT]
Roll a six-sided die and apply the result until the end of this turn.
● 1 or 2: This card loses 1000 ATK.
● 3 or 4: This card gains 600 ATK.
● 5 or 6: This card gains ATK equal to [the original ATK of 1 face-up monster on your opponent's field].

160016131.name: Animagica Witch
160016131.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Reveal up to 2 Level 7 or 8 LIGHT Attribute Effect Monsters in your hand to your opponent.
[EFFECT]
Draw cards equal to [the number of monsters revealed to meet the requirement]. Then, shuffle cards from your hand into the Deck equal to [the number of cards drawn by this effect].

160016158.name: Jointech Joint
160016158.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Shuffle 2 monsters from your Graveyard into the Deck.
[EFFECT]
Change 1 monster on your opponent's field to face-up Attack Position or face-down Defense Position. Then, you can Fusion Summon 1 Level 9 or lower EARTH Attribute or DARK Attribute Machine Type monster by sending monsters from your hand and/or field to the Graveyard as material.

160016159.name: Threat from Outer Space
160016159.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Pay 1000 LP.
[EFFECT]
Send the top card of your Deck to the Graveyard. Then, you can Set that card to your field (if it is a monster, you can Special Summon it in face-down Defense Position). Then, if you Special Summoned a Level 2 monster from the Graveyard by this effect, you can destroy 1 Spell/Trap Card on your opponent's field.

160017000.name: Five-Headed Dragon (Rush)
160017000.description:
5 Dragon Type monsters

Must be Fusion Summoned.

[REQUIREMENT]
None
[CONTINUOUS EFFECT]
This card cannot be destroyed by battle with a DARK, EARTH, WATER, FIRE, or WIND Attribute monster.

160017001.name: Stone Chariot Gravelriot
160017001.description: An ancient tank that drives with incredible balance. It shatters the balance of the enemy forces by penetrating a single point.

160017002.name: Gravebronze Dragon
160017002.description: A giant dragon that has a stately sheen. Its scales are said to grant the wishes of those that obtain them.

160017003.name: Hybridrive Scale
160017003.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
You have a LIGHT Attribute Dragon Type monster and an EARTH Attribute Machine Type monster in your Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Send the top card of your Deck to the Graveyard. Then, this turn, this face-up card can be treated as 2 Tributes for the Tribute Summon of a Dragon Type or Machine Type monster in Attack Position.

160017004.name: Hybridrive Tusk
160017004.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Send 1 card from your hand to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Send the top 3 cards of your Deck to the Graveyard. Then, you can add 1 "Hybridrive Screwdriver" from your Graveyard to your hand.

160017005.name: Hybridrive Lizard
160017005.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
During the turn you Normal Summoned this card.
[EFFECT]
Special Summon 1 "Hybridrive Scale" or 1 "Hybridrive Tusk" from your Graveyard to your field in face-up Defense Position.

160017006.name: Hybridrive Screwdriver
160017006.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Place 2 Dragon Type monsters and 2 Machine Type monsters from your Graveyard on the bottom of your Deck in any order.
[EFFECT]
Destroy 1 monster on the field. Then, neither player can Normal or Special Summon monsters with the same original name as the monster destroyed by this effect face-up until the end of your opponent's next turn.

160017007.name: Straynge Witch
160017007.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
You have no other monsters on your field.
[EFFECT]
Special Summon 1 "Sevens Road Charmy Witch" or "Sevens Road Witch" from your Graveyard face-up to your field. Then, you can add 1 "Fusion" from your Graveyard to your hand.

160017008.name: Lily Slayer
160017008.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
During the turn you Normal Summoned this card.
[EFFECT]
Send the top card of your Deck to the Graveyard. If you sent a Spellcaster Type monster to the Graveyard by this effect, this turn, this face-up card can be treated as 2 Tributes for the Tribute Summon of a DARK Attribute Spellcaster Type monster in Attack Position.

160017009.name: Chemipet Chirp
160017009.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
If you have no other monsters on your field, reveal 1 Pyro, Aqua, or Thunder Type monster in your hand.
[EFFECT]
Send the top 3 cards of your Deck to the Graveyard. Then, you can add to your hand 1 Pyro, Aqua, or Thunder Type monster from among the cards sent, with the same Level as [the Level of the monster revealed to meet the requirement].

160017010.name: Dice Key Mekuru
160017010.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Send 1 card from your hand to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Excavate the top 6 cards of your Deck. You can add 1 excavated "Dice Key Ribbon" or LIGHT Attribute monster with an effect that requires a die roll to your hand. Place the remaining cards on the bottom of your Deck in any order.

160017011.name: Dice Key Kuu
160017011.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
During the turn you Normal Summoned this card.
[EFFECT]
Add 1 "Dice Key Nel" from your Graveyard to your hand. Then, roll a six-sided die. If the result was 6, you can place 1 face-up Defense Position monster from your opponent's field on top of the owner's Deck.

160017012.name: Dice Key Ribbon
160017012.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Send this face-up card from your field to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Special Summon 1 "Dice Key Mekuru" or 1 LIGHT Attribute monster with an effect that requires a die roll from your Graveyard face-up to your field.

160017013.name: Cybersepice Hotpot
160017013.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
During your Main Phase that you Normal Summoned or Special Summoned this card.
[EFFECT]
Add 1 Level 7 or higher FIRE Attribute Cyberse Type monster or 1 "Spice Cross Mix" from your Graveyard to your hand.

160017014.name: Cybersepice Cinnamon
160017014.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
None
[EFFECT]
Your opponent excavates the top card of their Deck. Then, if that card is a Level 5 or higher monster, you can Special Summon 1 monster from your hand face-up to your field. Your opponent places the excavated card on the top of their Deck.

160017015.name: Cybersepice Turmeric
160017015.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
You have 10 or more cards in your Deck and have a face-up FIRE Attribute Cyberse Type monster other than this card on your field.
[EFFECT]
Look at 1 face-down card in your opponent's Spell & Trap Zone. Then, if that card is a Trap Card, draw 1 card.

160017016.name: Cybersepice Cumin
160017016.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
None
[EFFECT]
Your opponent excavates the top card of their Deck. If that card is a monster, inflict damage to your opponent equal to [its Level] x 100. Your opponent places the excavated card on the top of their Deck.

160017017.name: Wheatcloth Demeter
160017017.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
During a turn you have not Special Summoned a monster from the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Your opponent excavates the top 2 cards of their Deck. You can Special Summon 1 monster with a Level equal to or lower than [the total Levels of the excavated monsters] from your Graveyard face-up to your field. Your opponent places the excavated cards on the top of their Deck in any order.

160017018.name: Cybersepice Nutmeg
160017018.description:
You can Tribute Summon this card in Attack Position by Tributing 1 Cyberse Type monster.

[REQUIREMENT]
None
[EFFECT]
Each player sends the top card of their Deck to the Graveyard. Then, you can place 1 of the cards sent on either the top or bottom of the owner's Deck.

160017019.name: Cybersepice Garam Masala
160017019.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Your opponent has a face-up monster on their field.
[EFFECT]
Your opponent excavates the top 3 cards of their Deck. 1 face-up monster on your opponent's field loses ATK equal to [the total Levels of the excavated monsters] x 300 until the end of this turn. Your opponent places the excavated cards on the top of their Deck in any order.

160017020.name: Dark Matter Deadcheer
160017020.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
During the turn you Normal Summoned this card.
[EFFECT]
Send 1 monster from your field to the Graveyard. Then, you can Special Summon 1 Level 5 Galaxy Type monster with 1300 DEF from your Graveyard to your field in face-up Attack Position.

160017021.name: Dark Matter Lockdoll
160017021.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Send 1 DARK Attribute Galaxy Type monster with 1300 DEF from your hand to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
This card's name becomes "Dark Matter Mist" this turn. Then, you can draw 1 card.

160017022.name: Dark Matter Jelly
160017022.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
If you have another face-up DARK Attribute Galaxy Type monster on your field, send 1 face-down monster from your field to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Your opponent cannot activate Trap Cards during the Battle Phase this turn. Then, change this card to face-down Defense Position.

160017023.name: Dark Matter Craydoll
160017023.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Pay 500 LP.
[EFFECT]
This card's name becomes "Dark Matter Mist" this turn. Then, you can add 1 "Fusion" from your Graveyard to your hand.

160017024.name: Dark Matter String
160017024.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Reveal 1 Level 5 or lower DARK Attribute Galaxy Type monster with 1300 DEF in your hand.
[EFFECT]
Special Summon the monster revealed to meet the requirement to your field in face-up Attack Position or face-down Defense Position. Then, this card gains 700 ATK until the end of your opponent's next turn.

160017025.name: Dark Matter Knight
160017025.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
