160423008.name: Yormungarde (Rush)
160423008.description: An extremely long snake that dwells in the world of myth.

160423009.name: Emperor of the Land and Sea (Rush)
160423009.description: A reptilian monster that sprays fire in every direction.

160424001.name: Sevens Road Witch
160424001.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Send 1 card from your hand to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Special Summon 1 Level 7 or higher, DARK Attribute, Spellcaster Type monster from your hand, face-up to your field. If you Special Summoned "Sevens Road Magician" by this effect, this card gains 400 ATK until the end of this turn.

160424002.name: Illusion Strike Dragon Miragias
160424002.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Send 1 Level 7 or higher Dragon Type monster from your hand to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Up to 2 face-up Level 7 or lower monsters on your opponent's field lose 1500 ATK until the end of this turn. This turn, if this card destroyed a monster by battle, it can make a second attack on a monster during that Battle Phase.

160424007.name: Harpie Lady (Rush)
160424007.description: This human-shaped animal with wings is beautiful to watch but deadly in battle.

160424008.name: Winged Dragon, Guardian of the Fortress #1 (Rush)
160424008.description: A dragon commonly found guarding mountain fortresses. Its signature attack is a sweeping dive from out of the blue.

160425001.name: Transam Linac
160425001.description: Fight for the Light! Pure Finish!

160425006.name: Stone Dragon (Rush)
160425006.description: A dragon formed by huge boulders that are also used to attack the enemy.

160426005.name: Delight of the Mighty
160426005.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
When your opponent Normal Summons a monster.
[EFFECT]
1 face-up Normal Monster on your field gains ATK/DEF equal to [that Normal Summoned monster's Level] x 100 until the end of this turn.

160426006.name: Fancy Ladybug Pastel
160426006.description: A kindhearted ladybug whose trademark is the heart on its back. It is said that if you touch it, your love will come true.

160426007.name: Dream Ladybug Rainbow
160426007.description: A vibrant ladybug whose trademark are the stars on its back. Even today, it brings happiness while drawing a rainbow in its trail.

160426008.name: Archfiend Marmot of Nefariousness (Rush)
160426008.description: An air marmot that has a nefarious horn and wings. It attacks by throwing acorns.

160426009.name: Hero of the East (Rush)
160426009.description: Feel da strength ah dis sword-swingin' samurai from da Far East.

160426010.name: Frenzied Panda (Rush)
160426010.description: A savage beast that carries a big bamboo stick for beating down its enemies.

160427001.name: Strong Boy Sevens Road
160427001.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
If you have a monster in your Graveyard, send the top card of your Deck to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
This card gains ATK equal to [the number of different Attributes in your Graveyard] x 200, until the end of this turn. Then, if your opponent's LP are 700 or less, inflict 700,000,000 damage to your opponent.

160428001.name: Supreme Wildgleam Magnum Overlord [L]
160428001.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Maximum Mode
[CONTINUOUS EFFECT]
This card gains ATK equal to [the number of monsters on your opponent's field] x 500. If you have 10 or more monsters in your Graveyard, this card inflicts piercing battle damage (if the ATK of the attacking monster exceeds the DEF of the attack target, inflict the difference), if it attacks a Defense Position monster.

160428002.name: Supreme Wildgleam Magnum Overlord
160428002.description:
MAXIMUM ATK = 3500
You can Maximum Summon this card together with "Supreme Wildgleam Magnum Overlord [L]" and "Supreme Wildgleam Magnum Overlord [R]".

[REQUIREMENT]
Maximum Mode
[CONTINUOUS EFFECT]
This card cannot be destroyed by your opponent's Trap Card effects.

160428003.name: Supreme Wildgleam Magnum Overlord [R]
160428003.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Maximum Mode
[CONTINUOUS EFFECT]
During the turn your opponent Special Summoned a Level 5 or higher monster face-up, while this card is face-up, your opponent cannot activate the effects of face-up Level 10 or lower monsters.

160428004.name: Sturdy Strike Dragon Metagiastar F
160428004.description:
"Steel Strike Dragon Metagias" + "The Dragon"

[REQUIREMENT]
Send the top card of your Deck to the Graveyard.
[MULTI-CHOICE EFFECT]
● All face-up monsters on your field gain 500 ATK until the end of this turn, also this card can make up to 2 attacks on monsters this turn.
● All face-up monsters on your field cannot be destroyed by battle or your opponent's Trap Card effects until the end of this turn, also this card can attack twice this turn.

160428005.name: Magician of Dark Sevens
160428005.description:
"Sevens Road Magician" + "Darkness Zerorogue"

[REQUIREMENT]
None
[CONTINUOUS EFFECT]
This card gains ATK equal to [the number of DARK Attribute Spellcaster Type monsters in your Graveyard] x 300. You take no battle damage from battles involving your other monsters.

160428006.name: Darkness Zerorogue
160428006.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
You have 8 or more DARK Attribute Spellcaster Type monsters in your Graveyard during your Main Phase that you Special Summoned this card.
[EFFECT]
Destroy all face-up Level 8 or lower monsters on your opponent's field.

160428007.name: Darkness Fource Seeker
160428007.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
You have 3 or more DARK Attribute Spellcaster Type monsters with different Levels in your Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Send the top 4 cards of your Deck to the Graveyard. This turn, you can only attack with DARK Attribute Spellcaster Type monsters.

160428008.name: Darkness Rogue
160428008.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
You Normal Summoned this card this turn and have no other monsters on your field.
[EFFECT]
Special Summon 1 DARK Attribute Spellcaster Type monster from your hand face-up to your field. Then, place this card from your field on the bottom of the Deck.

160428009.name: Sevens Road Magician
160428009.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Send the top card of your Deck to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
This card gains ATK equal to [the number of different Attributes in your Graveyard] x 300, until the end of this turn.

160428010.name: Sevens Road Witch
160428010.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Send 1 card from your hand to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Special Summon 1 Level 7 or higher, DARK Attribute, Spellcaster Type monster from your hand, face-up to your field. If you Special Summoned "Sevens Road Magician" by this effect, this card gains 400 ATK until the end of this turn.

160428018.name: Magic Curtain
160428018.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Pay 1000 LP.
[EFFECT]
Special Summon 1 Spellcaster Type monster from your hand face-up to your field. It cannot be destroyed by your opponent's Trap Card effects this turn.

160428019.name: Road Magic - Dark Twilight
160428019.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
If you have a face-up Level 7 or higher Spellcaster Type monster on your field, send 1 DARK Attribute monster from your hand to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Destroy 1 face-up monster on your opponent's field.

160428020.name: Darkness Lode
160428020.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
None
[EFFECT]
While this card is face-up in the Field Zone, face-up Level 5 or higher DARK Attribute Spellcaster Type monsters on the field gain 400 ATK and lose 1500 DEF.

160428021.name: Sevens Road Protection
160428021.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
When your opponent Normal Summons a monster.
[EFFECT]
All face-up DARK Attribute Spellcaster Type monsters on your field cannot be destroyed by your opponent's card effects this turn. If you have "Sevens Road Magician" in your Graveyard, you can change that opponent's Normal Summoned monster to face-up Defense Position.

160428023.name: Magic Fire Guard
160428023.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
When an opponent's Level 8 or lower monster declares an attack while you have 2 or more Spellcaster Type monsters in your Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
1 Attack Position Spellcaster Type monster on your field cannot be destroyed by battle this turn.

160428024.name: Omega Guitarna the Shining Megastar
160428024.description:
"Prima Guitarna the Shining Superstar" + "Ama Lilith"

[REQUIREMENT]
Send the top card of your Deck to the Graveyard.
[MULTI-CHOICE EFFECT]
● This card gains ATK equal to [the number of monsters on your opponent's field] x 1000 until the end of this turn. This turn, this card cannot be destroyed by your opponent's Trap Card effects.
● Destroy 1 Spell/Trap Card on your opponent's field.

160428025.name: Princess Omega the Shining Megastar
160428025.description:
"Prima Guitarna the Shining Superstar" + "Ama Lilith"

[REQUIREMENT]
None
[MULTI-CHOICE EFFECT]
● Change the battle positions of all monsters on your field. Then, you can make 1 face-up monster on your opponent's field lose ATK equal to [the number of monsters on your field] x 800 until the end of this turn.
● Shuffle up to 7 cards from your opponent's Graveyard into the Deck.

160428027.name: CAN:D ALL
160428027.description:
"CAN:D" + "Ice Pop Bear"

[REQUIREMENT]
None
[EFFECT]
Special Summon 1 Level 6 or lower Psychic Type monster from your Graveyard face-up to your field.

160428029.name: CAN - Sp:D
160428029.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
If you have another face-up Omega Psychic or Psychic Type monster on your field, send the top card of your Deck to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
This turn, 1 face-up monster on your field gains 200 ATK and your opponent cannot activate Trap Cards when it declares an attack.

160428035.name: Progress Potter
160428035.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Shuffle 5 monsters from your Graveyard into the Deck.
[EFFECT]
Shuffle up to 2 cards from your opponent's Graveyard into the Deck. Then, you can draw cards equal to [the number of "Progress Potter" and "Pot of Avarice" with different names in your Graveyard].

160428037.name: Ice Pop Bear
160428037.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
During the turn you Normal Summoned this card.
[EFFECT]
Special Summon 1 "CAN:D" or "Ama Lilith" from your Graveyard face-up to your field. This turn, you can only attack with Omega Psychic or Psychic Type monsters.

160428042.name: Ama Lilith
160428042.description: A girl who freely plays her emotions into song. Her favorite feelings will never lose their color.

160428044.name: Psychic Omega Blast
160428044.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
If your opponent has 2 or more face-up monsters on their field, shuffle 4 Psychic Type monsters from your Graveyard into the Deck.
[EFFECT]
Destroy 1 face-up monster with the lowest ATK on your opponent's field. Then, if you have a face-up Omega Psychic Type monster on your field, inflict damage to your opponent equal to [the original ATK of the monster destroyed by this effect].

160428048.name: Cross Target
160428048.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
When an opponent's Level 8 or lower monster declares an attack while you have a face-up Level 7 or higher Omega Psychic or Psychic Type monster on your field.
[EFFECT]
Return the attacking monster to the hand. Then, if you have a face-up "Handy Lady" on your field, you can add 1 Level 3 or lower monster from your Graveyard to your hand.

160428049.name: Featuring Omega
160428049.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
When your opponent Special Summons a monster.
[EFFECT]
1 face-up Omega Psychic or Psychic Type monster on your field gains 1200 ATK until the end of this turn. Also, if that monster's Level is 9, it cannot be destroyed by battle or your opponent's card effects this turn.

160428052.name: Dian Keto the Cooking Master
160428052.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Send 1 card from your hand to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Send the top 3 cards of your Deck to the Graveyard. Then, if your LP are 2000 or less, you can gain LP equal to [the number of Aqua Type monsters sent to the Graveyard by this effect] x 1000.

160428053.name: Brick Phone Nyan Nyan
160428053.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
During the turn you Normal Summoned this card, place 1 card from your hand on the bottom of the Deck.
[EFFECT]
1 face-up monster on your opponent's field loses 500 ATK until the end of this turn. Then, you can add 1 Level 7 or higher Aqua Type monster from your Graveyard to your hand.

160428054.name: Fashion of Faith
160428054.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
You Normal Summoned this card this turn and have a face-up Level 7 or higher Aqua Type monster on your field.
[EFFECT]
Draw 1 card. Then, all face-up Level 7 or higher Aqua Type monsters on your field gain 400 ATK until the end of this turn.

160428056.name: Tiramisu Dark Witch
160428056.description: An angelic store attendant who carries both tiramisu and all the raging fads. Even against the ever-changing trends and the hearts of evil, she will never lose.

160428059.name: Frenzied Panda Cotta
160428059.description: A savage panda store clerk. It completely snaps when someone orders panna cotta.

160428061.name: Change of Dessert
160428061.description: An angel-like store attendant that's actually a demon. Her heart is jiggling like jelly, wondering whether to bring the order or not.

160428062.name: Mother's Storm
160428062.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
If you have a face-up Level 8 or higher Aqua Type monster on your field, send 1 Aqua Type monster from your hand to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Destroy 1 Level 8 or lower monster on your opponent's field. Then, if you destroyed a Machine Type monster by this effect, you can destroy all monsters on your opponent's field.

160428065.name: Bubbleburst Shock!
160428065.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
You have a face-up Level 8 or higher Aqua Type monster on your field.
[EFFECT]
Take damage equal to [the total ATK of all face-up Level 8 or lower monsters on your opponent's field]. Then, if you took damage by this effect, destroy all face-up Level 8 or lower monsters on your opponent's field.

160428067.name: Party Up
160428067.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
When an opponent's monster declares an attack targeting your face-up Aqua Type monster.
[EFFECT]
Gain LP equal to [the attacking monster's ATK].

160428068.name: Master's Cure
160428068.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
When your opponent Normal or Special Summons a Level 7 or higher monster face-up.
[EFFECT]
Gain 1000 LP. Then, you can make 1 face-up Aqua Type monster on your field gain 1000 ATK until the end of this turn.

160428071.name: Dark Doom Dread Ruler
160428071.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Send 1 Zombie Type monster from your hand to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
This card gains 1000 ATK until the end of this turn. Then, if you have a Level 7 Zombie Type monster in your Graveyard, inflict 700 damage to your opponent.

160428073.name: Crawling Torso
160428073.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
During the turn you Normal Summoned this card.
[EFFECT]
Add 1 Zombie Type Normal Monster with 0 ATK from your Graveyard to your hand.

160428074.name: Cyber-Stein Frankenshrine
160428074.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
If you have a Level 4 or lower Zombie Type Normal Monster in your Graveyard during the turn you Normal Summoned this card, send the top card of your Deck to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Special Summon up to 2 Level 4 or lower Zombie Type Normal Monsters from your Graveyard face-up to your field.

160428075.name: Ghoulish Gal
160428075.description: In the men's bathroom down in the basement, you'll suddenly feel a presence behind your back. But you know, you should absolutely not turn back until you've finished your business. If you happen to look back and end up seeing that monster...

160428076.name: The Thing In the Purple Mirror
160428076.description: Everyone... Do you know the phrase "purple mirror"? If you do know it, then be careful. If you don't forget it by the time you turn 20, then...

160428077.name: Doll of Dread
160428077.description: When you're sleeping in the dressing room, you'll feel a bit of sleep paralysis... In the darkness, if you squint your eyes at your bedside...

160428078.name: Samba Zombie Rio
160428078.description: A zombie that constantly shuffles around awkwardly. It has no sense of self left, but it hasn't forgotten the rhythm of the samba that seeped into its body.

160428079.name: Nightmare Knock
160428079.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Your opponent has 2 or more Spell/Trap Cards on their field.
[EFFECT]
Choose 1 Spell/Trap Card on your opponent's field, and destroy all other Spell/Trap Cards on their field. This turn, your monsters cannot attack.

160428080.name: Frightening Fan Mail
160428080.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
If your opponent has cards in their hand, change all Attack Position Zombie Type Normal Monsters on your field to face-up Defense Position.
[EFFECT]
Send random cards from your opponent's hand to the Graveyard, up to [the number of face-up Defense Position Zombie Type monsters on your field]. Then, inflict damage to your opponent equal to [the number of cards sent to the Graveyard by this effect] x 300.

160428081.name: Zombie Carnival
160428081.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
None
[EFFECT]
While this card is face-up in the Field Zone, face-up Zombie Type monsters on the field gain ATK/DEF equal to [the number of face-up Zombie Type monsters on the field] x 100.

160428082.name: Zombie Fireworks
160428082.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Reveal 1 Level 5 or higher Zombie Type monster in your hand.
[EFFECT]
Special Summon up to 2 Level 6 or lower Zombie Type monsters from your Graveyard face-up to your field. Then, send 1 Level 5 or higher Zombie Type monster from your hand to the Graveyard. This turn, you can only attack with Zombie Type monsters.

160428083.name: Surprising Zomvictory
160428083.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
You have 2 or more face-up Zombie Type Normal Monsters on your field.
[EFFECT]
Change the battle positions of up to 3 monsters on your opponent's field. Then, you can make all face-up Zombie Type monsters on your field gain ATK equal to [the number of Zombie Type Normal Monsters in your Graveyard] x 100 until the end of this turn.

160428084.name: It's Right Behind You!
160428084.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
When your opponent takes damage during the Draw Phase or Main Phase.
[EFFECT]
Special Summon 1 "Dark Doom Dread Ruler" or 1 "Wicked Shadow Dark Lurker" from your hand or Graveyard face-up to your field. Switch its original ATK/DEF until the end of this turn.

160428085.name: I Hear Footsteps
160428085.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
When your opponent draws for their normal draw in their Draw Phase while you have a face-up Zombie Type monster on your field.
[EFFECT]
Look at your opponent's hand. You can choose up to 3 Spell/Trap Cards from their hand. If you do, your opponent Sets those cards to their field, and they take damage equal to [the number of cards Set by this effect] x 300.

160428086.name: The Cursed Cat Counting Dishes
160428086.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
When an opponent's Level 9 or lower monster declares an attack while you have a face-up Level 7 or higher Zombie Type monster on your field.
[EFFECT]
Negate the attack.

160428087.name: Terrorphone Number
160428087.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
When your opponent draws for their normal draw in their Draw Phase while you have a Zombie Type monster in your Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Inflict 900 damage to your opponent. This turn, if your opponent attacks a face-up monster, they can only attack the monster on your field with the lowest Level.

160428088.name: Oriental Tiger
160428088.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Change this card's battle position (Attack Position becomes face-up Defense Position, Defense Position becomes face-up Attack Position).
[EFFECT]
Inflict damage to your opponent equal to [the number of Spell/Trap Cards in their Graveyard] x 100. Then, if your opponent has 10 or more Spell Cards in their Graveyard, inflict 1200 damage to your opponent.

160428089.name: Shadow Ghoul (Rush)
160428089.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
None
[CONTINUOUS EFFECT]
This card gains ATK equal to [the number of monsters in your Graveyard] x 100.

160428090.name: Cursed Skeletal Dragon Diarga
160428090.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
If you have another face-up Zombie Type monster on your field, send this face-up card from your field to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
1 face-up Level 5 or higher monster on your opponent's field loses 1000 ATK until the end of this turn.

160428091.name: Peeking Magician
160428091.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Send the top card of your Deck to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Each player excavates the top 2 cards of their Deck. Then, they place their excavated cards on top of their Deck in any order.

160428092.name: Specter of Heaven's End
160428092.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
None
[EFFECT]
Excavate the top 3 cards of your Deck. Send 1 excavated card to the Graveyard. Then, shuffle the remaining cards into the Deck.

160428093.name: Magical Ghost (Rush)
160428093.description: This creature casts a spell of terror and confusion just before attacking its enemies.

160428094.name: Sacrificial Summon
160428094.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Send 1 face-up monster with 1600 or more ATK from your field to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Special Summon 1 Effect Monster from your hand face-up to your field. If you sent an Effect Monster whose original Level is 7 or higher to the Graveyard to meet the requirement, the monster Special Summoned by this effect can make up to 2 attacks on monsters this turn.

160428096.name: Trade-In (Rush)
160428096.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Send 1 Level 8 monster from your hand to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Draw 2 cards.

160428098.name: Imptailing Crisis
160428098.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
When an opponent's monster declares an attack.
[EFFECT]
Inflict 600 damage to your opponent. Then, if your opponent has 2 or more face-up Level 7 monsters on their field, you can shuffle 1 monster from your opponent's field into the Deck.

160428099.name: Recurring Nightmare (Rush)
160428099.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
None
[EFFECT]
Add 2 DARK Attribute monsters with 0 DEF from your Graveyard to your hand.

160428100.name: Pot of Avarice (Rush)
160428100.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Shuffle 5 monsters from your Graveyard into the Deck.
[EFFECT]
Draw 2 cards.

160429001.name: Luster Dragon (Rush)
160429001.description: A very beautiful dragon covered with sapphire. It does not like fights, but has incredibly high attack power.

160429002.name: Thestalos the Firestorm Monarch (Rush)
160429002.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
During the turn you Tribute Summoned this card in Attack Position.
[EFFECT]
Send 1 random card from your opponent's hand to the Graveyard. Then, if you sent a monster to the Graveyard by this effect, inflict damage to your opponent equal to [that monster's Level] x 100.

160429003.name: Luster Dragon #2 (Rush)
160429003.description: This dragon feeds on emerald. Enchanted by this monster even when attacked, few people live to tell of its beauty.

160430001.name: Curse of Dragon (Rush)
160430001.description: A wicked dragon that taps into dark forces to execute a powerful attack.

160430002.name: Mystical Sandbox
160430002.description: A spellcaster who controls water and can harden sand. She creates all kinds of things with her muddy hands.

160430003.name: Kanan the Beautiful Swordmistress
160430003.description: A lady swordmaster whose main battlefield is the theater club. Armed with a sword and shield, she floats like a butterfly and dances like a bee.

160430006.name: Spirit of the Mini Harp
160430006.description: A spirit that soothes the soul with the music of its music class harp.

160430007.name: Mean Mutt Chihuahua Warrior
160430007.description: A Mean Mutt that catches its enemies off guard with its large and round cute eyes, causing them to leave their purses, pockets, and wallets unguarded. His loyalty is... so-so.

160430008.name: Psychic Kappa (Rush)
160430008.description: An amphibian with a myriad of powers to shield it from enemy attacks.

160430009.name: Kappa Rapper
160430009.description: A Kappa whose sick rhymes cause people to approach the water's edge.

160430010.name: Kappa Avenger (Rush)
160430010.description: An amphibian that sold his soul for unlimited power to avenge his late friend.

160431001.name: Transam Linac
160431001.description: Fight for the Light! Pure Finish!

160431002.name: Galactica Oblivion
160431002.description: War To Zen! Awesome True Goodnight!

160431003.name: Jointech Rex
160431003.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
During the turn you Normal Summoned this card, shuffle 3 monsters from your Graveyard into the Deck.
[EFFECT]
Destroy 1 card in your opponent's Spell & Trap Zone.

160431004.name: Blue-Fang Burst Dragon
160431004.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Send the top card of your Deck to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Destroy all face-up monsters with 1500 or less ATK on your opponent's field. Then, this card gains ATK equal to [the number of monsters destroyed by this effect] x 300 until the end of this turn.

160431005.name: Chemicalized Salamander
160431005.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Shuffle 3 Pyro Type monsters from your Graveyard into the Deck.
[EFFECT]
All face-up monsters on your opponent's field lose ATK equal to [the number of monsters in your opponent's Graveyard] x 100 until the end of this turn.

160431006.name: Voidvelg Requiem
160431006.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Send the top card of your Deck to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
This card gains ATK equal to [the number of face-up DARK Attribute monsters on your field] x 300 until the end of this turn. Then, if your opponent has a face-up LIGHT Attribute monster on their field, this card gains 600 ATK until the end of this turn.

160431007.name: Princess of the Flock - Miss Mutton
160431007.description: Baa-dum, baa-dum, baa-dum, baa-dum, baaaaa-dum! The sheep's in the meadow, the cow's in the corn! You can call me "miss", but I'm actually Wooly Wonderland royalty. I'm never sheepish about chowing on paper (even if it happens to be an important letter).

160432001.name: Greystorm Reverie
160432001.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Send 1 other card from your field to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
This card gains 500 ATK until the end of this turn. Also, if no Spell/Trap Cards are on the field, this card can make up to 2 attacks on monsters this turn.

160432002.name: Magician's Valkyria (Rush)
160432002.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
None
[CONTINUOUS EFFECT]
Your opponent cannot attack other face-up Spellcaster Type monsters.

160432003.name: Heavy Storm (Rush)
160432003.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
None
[EFFECT]

Pay 1000 LP.

Add 1 Level 4 or lower LIGHT Attribute Normal Monster or 1 "Praime Call" from your Graveyard to your hand, and this card gains 500 ATK until the end of this turn.

160452014.name: Voidvelg Elysium
160452014.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Send 1 card from your hand to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Change 1 face-up monster on your opponent's field to face-down Defense Position. This card gains 500 ATK until the end of this turn. Also, if you sent a monster to the Graveyard to meet the requirement, this card cannot be destroyed by your opponent's Trap Card effects this turn.

160452015.name: Nobody Scat Thief
160452015.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
When a monster on your field is destroyed by an opponent's attack or their card effect.
[EFFECT]
Draw 3 cards. Then, send 1 or more cards from your hand to the Graveyard. Then, if you have no monsters on your field, you take no battle damage from your opponent's Level 8 or lower monsters' attacks this turn.

160452016.name: Whispering Fairy
160452016.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Send 1 card from your hand to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Shuffle up to 2 monsters from your opponent's Graveyard into the Deck.

160452017.name: Deity of Seven Treasures - Ryozai
160452017.description:
If you have a monster with 2700 DEF or "Ship of Seven Treasures" in your Graveyard, you can Special Summon this card from your hand face-up to your field.

[REQUIREMENT]
None
[CONTINUOUS EFFECT]
Face-up Level 7 monsters on your field and face-down Spell/Trap Cards on your field cannot be destroyed by your opponent's card effects.

160452018.name: Praime Claw Girl
160452018.description:
You can Tribute Summon this card in Attack Position by Tributing 1 monster. If you do, its original ATK becomes 200.

[REQUIREMENT]
Place 2 cards from your hand on the bottom of the Deck in any order.
[EFFECT]
Special Summon 1 LIGHT Attribute Normal Monster from your Graveyard to your field in face-up Defense Position. Then, you can add 1 "Fusion" from your Graveyard to your hand.

160452019.name: Meteor Swarm Entry Dragon
160452019.description: "Meteor Drake" + 1 Level 6 or higher EARTH Attribute or DARK Attribute monster

160452020.name: Elemental Circulation
160452020.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Reveal 1 Level 6 or 7 Warrior Type Fusion Monster in your Extra Deck to your opponent and send 1 Warrior Type monster whose name is mentioned as material on that monster from your hand to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Draw 3 cards. Then, send 1 card from your hand to the Graveyard. You cannot activate monster effects for the rest of this turn, except those of Warrior Type monsters.

160452021.name: Dragon Knight of Darkness
160452021.description: A dragon knight leading a dark army. His merciless attacks have unparalleled strength, and the cursed sword he wields devours the souls of his foes and makes him stronger.

160452022.name: Etraynze the Shadow Flower Restricter
160452022.description:
This card's name becomes "Etraynze the Shadow Flower Ninja" while in the Graveyard.

[REQUIREMENT]
Place 1 Plant Type monster from your Graveyard on the bottom of the Deck.
[EFFECT]
This card's name becomes the same as the name of 1 Plant Type monster in your Graveyard this turn. Then, you can Set 1 "Fusion" from your Graveyard in your Spell & Trap Zone.

160452023.name: Support Unit - Kumamimi
160452023.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
None
[CONTINUOUS EFFECT]
Face-up EARTH Attribute Machine Type monsters on your field gain 500 ATK, and they inflict piercing battle damage.

160452024.name: The Ultimate Blue-Eyed Legend
160452024.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
None
[EFFECT]
Fusion Summon a Level 10 or higher Dragon Type monster by sending up to 3 Dragon Type monsters from your hand and/or field to the Graveyard as material. This turn, the monster Special Summoned by this effect cannot be destroyed by your opponent's card effects.

160452025.name: Invitation to a Delirious Dream
160452025.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
When your opponent Normal or Special Summons a monster, place 1 monster from your field and 1 card from your hand on the bottom of the owner's Deck in any order.
[EFFECT]
Take control of 1 face-up Level 8 or lower monster on your opponent's field, except a Maximum Monster. While the monster you took control by this effect is face-up on the field, it cannot attack or activate its effects.

160452026.name: Card Defender
160452026.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
None
[CONTINUOUS EFFECT]
During your opponent's turn, Spell/Trap Cards on your field cannot be returned to the hand, Deck, or Extra Deck by card effects. If you have a face-up Warrior Type Normal Monster or Warrior Type Fusion Monster on your field, face-up monsters on your field gain 1000 ATK.

160452027.name: Justiciar of the Dragon Stream
160452027.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Shuffle 1 "Justiciar of the Dragon Stream" or 4 monsters from your Graveyard into the Deck.
[EFFECT]
Destroy 1 face-down card in your opponent's Spell & Trap Zone.

160452028.name: Sevens Road Charmy Witch
160452028.description:
"Sevens Road Witch" + 1 Level 1 EARTH Attribute Spellcaster Type monster

[REQUIREMENT]
Send the top card of your Deck to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Change the battle position of 1 monster on your opponent's field (Attack Position becomes face-up Defense Position, Defense Position becomes face-up Attack Position). Then, this turn, this card inflicts piercing battle damage. Then, if "Sevens Road Magician" is in your Graveyard, this turn, this card cannot be destroyed by card effects.

160452029.name: Black Magic Ritual (Rush)
160452029.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
None
[EFFECT]
Ritual Summon "Magician of Black Chaos" by sending monsters from your hand and/or field to the Graveyard whose total Levels equal 8 or more as material (you cannot use more monsters than necessary as material).

160452030.name: Repulsive Force
160452030.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
When your opponent Normal or Special Summons a monster, or when an opponent's monster declares an attack, shuffle 3 Rock Type monsters from your Graveyard into the Deck.
[EFFECT]
Change 1 face-up monster on your opponent's field to face-down Defense Position.

160453000.name: Cocopudding the Princess of Happiness
160453000.description: She is the princess of “Coco”, a kingdom overflowing with happiness, and is adored by all for her gentle personality. She brings smiles to those that arrives, and blesses those who depart. She has a strong bond with her attendants “Caramel” and “Whip”.

160453001.name: Sevens Road Witch
160453001.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Send 1 card from your hand to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Special Summon 1 Level 7 or higher, DARK Attribute, Spellcaster Type monster from your hand, face-up to your field. If you Special Summoned "Sevens Road Magician" by this effect, this card gains 400 ATK until the end of this turn.

160453002.name: Yamiruler the Dark Delayer
160453002.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
During the turn you Normal Summoned this card, change its battle position (Attack Position becomes face-up Defense Position, Defense Position becomes face-up Attack Position).
[EFFECT]
Until the end of the opponent's next turn, while this card is face-up, neither player can Tribute Summon Level 7 or higher monsters.

160453003.name: Royal Rebel's Heavy Metal
160453003.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
During the turn you Normal Summoned this card by Tributing a Level 5 or higher monster.
[EFFECT]
Choose 1 face-up Level 8 or lower monster with the lowest Level on your opponent's field, and this card gains ATK equal to [that monster's ATK] until the end of this turn. Destroy that monster.

160453004.name: Transam Linac
160453004.description: Fight for the Light! Pure Finish!

160453005.name: Voidvelg Requiem
160453005.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
Send the top card of your Deck to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
This card gains ATK equal to [the number of face-up DARK Attribute monsters on your field] x 300 until the end of this turn. Then, if your opponent has a face-up LIGHT Attribute monster on their field, this card gains 600 ATK until the end of this turn.

160453006.name: Ember the Super Assistant
160453006.description: My favorite experiment is flame color reactions! I'm gonna work hard all day today, powered by my burning spirit!

160453007.name: Cocosh the Spellcaster of Happiness
160453007.description: A spellcaster with a warm heart that brings smiles to people the world over with her legendary magic power of "Danishes". For her gracious deeds she was granted the name "Coco", though she also has a mischievous side where she dotes on her companion "Maple".

160454001.name: Cat in Cobra's Clothing
160454001.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
During the turn you Normal Summoned this card.
[EFFECT]
Send the top card of your Deck to the Graveyard. Then, if you sent a Level 9 or lower monster with 100 or more ATK to the Graveyard by this effect, while this card is face-up, it gains ATK equal to [the ATK of the monster sent to the Graveyard by this effect].

160455005.name: Momyu the Sea Shadow Spirit
160455005.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
During the turn you Normal Summoned this card, send 2 cards from your hand to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Take control of 1 face-down monster on your opponent's field (move it to your field, and use it yourself).

160455006.name: Mythical Chimera Snake
160455006.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
During the turn you Normal Summoned this card, send the top 2 cards of your Deck to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Shuffle up to 2 cards from your opponent's Graveyard into the Deck. Then, if you sent a WIND Attribute monster to the Graveyard to meet the requirement, you can inflict 400 damage to your opponent.

160455010.name: Gekka the Shadow Flower Beauty
160455010.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
During the turn you Normal Summoned this card, pay 500 LP.
[EFFECT]
Add 1 EARTH Attribute Plant Type Normal Monster from your Graveyard to your hand.

160455011.name: Etraynze the Shadow Flower Ninja
160455011.description:
[REQUIREMENT]
You have "Etraynze the Shadow Flower Ninja" in your Graveyard.
[EFFECT]
Send 1 Plant Type monster from your hand to the Graveyard. Then, Special Summon 1 "Etraynze the Shadow Flower Ninja" from your Graveyard face-up to your field, but place it on the bottom of the Deck during the End Phase. This turn, this card cannot attack directly.
